C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NDTV%20report%2C%20officials%20said%20at%20least%20800%20roads%20are%20blocked%20in%20the%20state%20due%20to%20landslides%20and%20the%20state%20has%20suffered%20losses%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20this%20monsoon%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20said%20his%20state%20would%20take%20a%20year%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20damage%20incurred%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20monsoon%20season%20and%20the%20estimated%20loss%20in%20the%20two%20devastating%20spells%20of%20heavy%20rain%20%E2%80%93%20this%20week%20and%20in%20July%20%E2%80%93%20is%20about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%2C%20NDTV%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20have%20witnessed%20dozens%20of%20deaths%20this%20monsoon%20and%20are%20set%20to%20receive%20more%20rain%2C%20according%20to%20weather%20forecasts%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20declare%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20a%20disaster-hit%20state%2C%20NDTV%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692189741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16180657%2Fcc4e44da-c1e7-4940-ad70-14a9cb35e957.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhimachal-pradesh-another-landslide-in-shimla-death-toll-climbs-to-60%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20search%20and%20rescue%20operation%20was%20initiated%20with%20sniffer%20dogs%20and%20rescue%20personnel%20present%20at%20the%20site.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fhimachal-pradesh-another-landslide-in-sh