expects%20a%20repeat%20of%20last%20year's%20sharp%20decline%20in%20stocks%20as%20risks%20mount%20in%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20economist%20sees%20several%20headwinds%20including%20Fitch%20and%20Moody's%20downgrades%20and%20Chinese%20deflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20way%20overvalued%20by%20historical%20standards%20and%20relative%20to%20other%20assets%2C%20Rosenberg%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20ready%20for%20a%20repeat%20of%20last%20year's%20slump%20in%20stocks%2C%20as%20investors%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20mounting%20risks%20in%20markets%20today%2C%20David%20Rosenberg%20has%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rosenberg%20Research%20president%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-deflation-markets-property-real-estate-housing-beijing-2023-8%5C%22%3Edeflation%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20higher%20borrowing%20costs%20for%20the%20US%20government%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Ffitch-debt-rating-downgrade-stock-market-crash-recession-joe-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3EFitch%20downgraded%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20country's%20credit%20rating%2C%20and%20a%20looming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcredit-crunch-us-bank-crisis-stock-corporate-earnings-recession-svb-2023-4%5C%22%3Ecredit%20crunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Moody's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbank-downgrades-explained-moodys-lowers-ratings-for-10-us-lenders-2023-8%5C%22%3Ecut%20the%20credit%20ratings%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20several%20US%20regional%20banks.%20He%20also%20singled%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstudent-loan-payments-restart-debt-fear-pressure-consumers-economy-survey-2023-6%5C%22%3Eresumption%20of%20student-loan%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%20as%20a%20likely%20drag%20on%20young%20Americans'%20future%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stock%20market%20simply%20does%20not%20understand%2C%20or%20more%20charitably%20does%20not%20appreciate%2C%26quot%3B%20those%20headwinds%2C%20Rosenberg%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqbunoro-31w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20uploaded%20to%20his%20firm's%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20one%20thing%20if%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20priced%20for%20these%20imperfections%2C%20but%20instead%20it%20is%20priced%20for%20perfection%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20chief%20North%20American%20economist%20at%20Merrill%20Lynch%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20explained%20that%20the%20equity-risk%20premium%2C%20or%20the%20projected%20difference%20in%20returns%20from%20stocks%20versus%20safe%20assets%20like%20government%20bonds%2C%20has%20tumbled%20to%20two-decade%20lows.%20Moreover%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies'%20valuations%20are%20in%20the%20top%209%25%20of%20expensiveness%20in%20the%20index's%20history%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20economist%20noted%20his%20firm's%20Strategizer%20tool%2C%20which%20models%20future%20returns%20for%20different%20assets%20and%20markets%2C%20is%20now%20showing%20its%20lowest%20score%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20since%20January%202022.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20benchmark%20index%20slumped%20nearly%2030%25%20during%20the%20next%20nine%20months%20last%20year%2C%20as%20price-to-earnings%20multiples%20receded%20toward%20historical%20averages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20expect%20a%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu%2C%20especially%20with%20interest%20rates%20so%20much%20higher%20than%20they%20were%20back%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20should%20avoid%20the%20%26quot%3Buber-expensive%26quot%3B%20US%20stock%20market%2C%20and%20instead%20buy%20%26quot%3Bundervalued%20and%20deeply%20shorted%26quot%3B%20US%20Treasuries%2C%20Rosenberg%20argued.%20He%20also%20touted%20stocks%20in%20Canada%20and%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20excluding%20China%20given%20the%20geopolitical%20risks%20of%20parking%20money%20there%20now%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20as%20well%20as%20gold%2C%20a%20traditional%20haven%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-bubbles-economy-recession-david-rosenberg-consumer-spending-2023-7%5C%22%3Epounding%20the%20alarm%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20stocks%20and%20economic%20risks%20for%20a%20while.%20In%20a%20recent%20research%20note%2C%20he%20compared%20the%20current%20hype%20around%20stocks%20to%20the%20mania%20that%20preceded%20the%20Great%20Crash%20of%201929%2C%20the%20dot-com%20bubble's%20implosion%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20and%20the%20housing%20market's%20collapse%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20warned%20that%20American%20consumers%20are%20burning%20through%20their%20savings%20and%20racking%20up%20credit-card%20debt%20as%20they%20weather%20historic%20inflation%20and%20sharply%20higher%20interest%20rates.%20They're%20now%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20end%20of%20the%20rope%2C%26quot%3B%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20painful%20recession%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-crash-spx-david-rosenberg-china-downgrades-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692189282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61571d21b414c10018634e83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-crash-spx-david-rosenberg-china-downgrades-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investors%20are%20ignoring%20headwinds%20such%20as%20Chinese%20deflation%2C%20a%20looming%20credit%20crunch%2C%20and%20mounting%20press