0in%20his%20open%20letter.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20abject%20disregard%20for%20civilized%20conduct%20makes%20San%20Francisco%20unlivable%20for%20its%20residents%2C%20unsafe%20for%20our%20employees%2C%20and%20unwelcoming%20to%20visitors%20from%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsfgov.org%2Fscorecards%2Fpublic-safety%2Fviolent-crime-rate-and-property-crime-rate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EStatistics%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20City%20and%20County%20of%20San%20Francisco%20suggest%20that%2C%20though%20crime%20rates%20fluctuate%20each%20year%20and%20the%20number%20of%20reported%20robberies%20has%20been%20falling%20since%202017%2C%20there%20have%20been%20more%20incidents%20of%20burglary%20and%20motor%20vehicle%20theft%20since%20the%20pandemic%20started.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsfgov.org%2Fscorecards%2Fpublic-safety%2Fpolice-response-serious-incidents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EData%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20City%20and%20County%20of%20San%20Francisco%20also%20shows%20that%20since%202016%2C%20police%20in%20the%20city%20have%20been%20getting%20slower%20to%20respond%20to%20high-priority%20calls%2C%20such%20as%20live%20gunshots%2C%20in-progress%20burglaries%2C%20and%20multi-car%20pile-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20recent%20criticism%20of%20San%20Francisco%20has%20centered%20around%20perceptions%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20public%20drug%20use%20and%20the%20number%20of%20unsheltered%20homeless%20people.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsf.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2022-10%2FSubstance_Use_Report_SF_2021_FINAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EStatistics%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20City%20and%20County%20of%20San%20Francisco's%20Department%20of%20Public%20Health%20suggest%20that%20the%20number%20of%20o