ernment%20today%2C%20a%20day%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-big-obc-outreach-pm-announces-scheme-to-help-traditional-workers-4299623%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%2C%20his%20last%20before%20next%20year's%20national%20election.%20The%20scheme%20will%20receive%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20for%20five%20years%20and%20cover%2018%20traditional%20trades%20to%20start%20with%2C%20said%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2030%20lakh%20people%20and%20their%20families%2C%20mainly%20from%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20scheme%2C%20said%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20scheme%2C%20artisans%20and%20craftsmen%20will%20be%20given%20recognition%20through%20the%20PM%20Vishwakarma%20certificate%20and%20ID%20card.%20They%20will%20be%20provided%20credit%20support%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh%20(first%20tranche)%20and%20Rs%202%20lakh%20(second%20tranche)%2C%20with%20a%20concessional%20interest%20rate%20of%205%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beneficiaries%20will%20also%20be%20provided%20skill%20upgradation%2C%20tool%20kits%2C%20an%20incentive%20for%20digital%20transactions%2C%20and%20marketing%20support%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20chaired%20by%20PM%20Modi%20approved%20the%20%26quot%3BPM%20Vishwakarma%26quot%3B%20along%20with%20other%20measures.%20The%20scheme%20will%20benefit%2030%20lakh%20craftsmen%20and%20their%20families%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-barbers-masons-potters-minister-on-pms-rs-15-000-crore-scheme-4300829%5C%22%3EPM%20Vishwakarma%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20artisans%20and%20craftspeople%20will%20be%20provided%20recognition%20through%20PM%20Vishwakarma%20certificates%2C%20ID%20cards%2C%20credit%20support%20upto%20Rs%201%20lakh%20(in%20the%20first%20tranche)%20and%20Rs%202%20lakh%20(in%20the%20second%20tranche)%20with%20a%20concessional%20interest%20rate%20of%205%25.%20The%20scheme%20will%20further%20provide%20skill%20upgradation%2C%20toolkit%20incentive%2C%20incentive%20for%20digital%20transactions%2C%20and%20marketing%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20%26quot%3BPM%20Vishwakarma%26quot%3B%20include%20carpenters%2C%20boat%20makers%2C%20blacksmiths%2C%20locksmiths%2C%20goldsmiths%2C%20potters%2C%20sculptors%2C%20cobblers%2C%20and%20masons%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20CCEA%20also%20greenlit%20the%20%26quot%3BPM-eBus%20Sewa%26quot%3B%20under%20which%2010%2C000%20e-buses%20will%20be%20added%20to%20the%20country's%20fleet%20and%20operations%20will%20be%20supported%20for%2010%20years%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B10%2C000%20e-buses%20will%20be%20deployed%20in%20169%20cities%20and%20infrastructure%20will%20be%20upgraded%20in%20181%20cities%20under%20the%20Green%20Urban%20Mobility%20Initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cabinet%20has%20approved%20the%20%26quot%3BPM-eBus%20Sewa%26quot%3B%20to%20augment%20city%20bus%20operations%20by%2010%2C000%20e-buses%20on%20a%20Private-Public%20Partnership%20model.%20%C2%A0The%20scheme%20would%20have%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs%2057%2C613%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20support%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20provided%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20The%20scheme%20will%20support%20bus%20operations%20for%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20scheme%20will%20generate%2045%2C000%20to%2055%2C000%20direct%20jobs%20through%20the%20deployment%20of%20around%2010%2C000%20buses%20in%20city%20bus%20operations%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20has%20two%20segments%20-%20%C2%A0one%20to%20augment%20the%20city%20bus%20services%20and%20the%20other%20to%20develop%20infra%20under%20the%20Green%20Urban%20Mobility%20Initiatives%20which%20envisages%20green%20initiatives%20like%20bus%20priority%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20multimodal%20interchange%20facilities%20among%20other%20things%2C%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20scheme%2C%20states%2Fcities%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20running%20the%20bus%20services%20and%20making%20payments%20to%20the%20bus%20operators.%20The%20central%20government%20will%20support%20these%20bus%20operations%20by%20providing%20a%20subsidy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM-eBus%20Sewa%20will%20boost%20e-mobility%2C%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692188100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Facp4kkig_ashwini-vaishnaw-pti_625x300_06_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-lakh-loan-with-maximum-5-interest-under-vishwakarma-scheme-centre-4302291%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20%26quot%3BPM%20Vishwakarma%26quot%3B%20scheme%20for%20artisans%20and%20craftsmen%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20government%20today%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20it%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%2C%20his%20last%20before%20next%20year's%20national%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-lakh-loan-with-maximum-5-interest-under-vishwakarma-scheme-centre-4302291%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-lakh-loan-with-maximum-5-interest-under-vishwakarma-scheme-centre-4302291%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-lakh-loan-with-maximum-5-in