overnment%20backed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Since%20then%2C%20both%20factions%20are%20in%20tussle%20to%20control%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20sparked%20speculation%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20may%20be%20trying%20to%20convince%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20a%20key%20face%20of%20opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20to%20shift%20his%20allegiance.%20Mr%20Pawar%20later%20said%20some%20%26quot%3Bwell-wishers%26quot%3B%20were%20trying%20to%20convince%20him%20to%20tie%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20added%20that%20he%20had%20no%20such%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Mr%20Chavan's%20remark%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20today%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20the%20former%20CM%20said.%20There%20was%20no%20such%20discussion.%20I%20am%20not%20denying%20that%20meeting%20happened%2C%20but%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20family%2C%20I%20speak%20to%20all%20family%20members.%20These%20are%20just%20rumors%20but%20there's%20no%20reality%20in%20any%20of%20these%20things%20being%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20seniormost%20person%20in%20the%20party%2C%20who%20will%20give%20me%20an%20offer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20too%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20had%20stressed%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20his%20nephew%20and%20it%20is%20natural%20for%20them%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20led%20to%20unease%20within%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20NCP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray).%20Sanjay%20Raut%2C%20MP%20and%20aide%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20has%20said%20Mr%20Pawar%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BBhishma%20Pitamaha%26quot%3B%20of%20Maharashtra%20politics%20and%20he%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20do%20anything%20that%20creates%20doubt%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tension%20within%20the%20alliance%20is%20unwelcome%20especially%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20Mumb