end%20of%20attacks%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20based%20on%20claims%20published%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%20how%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0had%20on%20August%207%20cited%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20claim%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20owner%2C%20issued%20a%20statement%20denying%20%E2%80%9Cany%20insinuation%20that%20%5BNewsClick%5D%20function%5Bs%5D%20as%20a%20mouth-piece%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20or%20other%20interests%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20BJP%20MPs%20and%20mainstream%20media%20channels%20soon%20afterwards%20shared%20and%20highlighted%20the%20NYT%20piece%20multiple%20times%20to%20attack%20the%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20Newsclick%E2%80%99s%20Twitter%20account%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclicks-twitter-account-suspended-days-after-bjp-mps-chinese-links-allegation%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20has%20now%20been%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signatories%20include%20senior%20journalists%2C%20activists%2C%20judges%2C%20lawyers%2C%20academics%2C%20scientists%2C%20writers%2C%20artists%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20actors%20and%20other%20concerned%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20signatories%20are%20journalists%20N.%20Ram%2C%20Prem%20Shankar%20Jha%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20and%20M.K.%20Venu%20(founding%20editors%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Sudheendra%20Kulkarni%2C%20P.%20Sainath%2C%20and%20Vaishna%20Roy%20(editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20activists%20John%20Dayal%2C%20Bezwada%20Wilson%20(national%20convenor%20of%20the%20Safai%20Karmachari%20Andolan)%2C%20Syeda%20Hameed%2C%20Harsh%20Mander%20and%20Aruna%20Roy%20(of%20the%20Mazdoor%20Kisan%20Shakti%20Sangathan)%2C%20legal%20practitioners%20Sanjay%20Hegde%2C%20Justice%20K.%20Chandru%2C%20Colin%20Gonsalves%2C%20and%20Prashant%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriters%20and%20academics%20K.%20Satchidanandan%2C%20Jerry%20Pinto%2C%20Damodar%20Mauzo%2C%20Romila%20Thapar%2C%20Sumit%20Sarkar%2C%20K.%20M.%20Shrimali%2C%20Tanika%20Sarkar%2C%20Prabhat%20Patnaik%2C%20Utsa%20Patnaik%2C%20Jayati%20Ghosh%2C%20C.P.%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20Zoya%20Hasan%2C%20and%20Jean%20Dreze%2C%20and%20film%20personalities%20Ratna%20Pathak%20Shah%2C%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%2C%20and%20Anand%20Patwardhan%20are%20also%20among%20signatories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20calls%20accusations%20against%20Newclick%20and%20its%20founder%20and%20editor-in-chief%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20%E2%80%9Cspurious%E2%80%9D%20and%20highlights%20that%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20which%20triggered%20these%20attacks%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20allege%20any%20violation%20of%20law%20by%20Newsclick.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20says%20that%20the%20news%20portal%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20the%20most%20oppressed%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20its%20inception%2C%20Newsclick%20has%20provided%20critical%20coverage%20of%20government%20policies%20and%20actions%20and%20their%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20our%20countrymen%20and%20women%2C%20focusing%20particularly%20on%20the%20struggles%20of%20the%20most%20oppressed%20and%20exploited%20sections%20of%20our%20society%2C%20its%20workers%20and%20peasants.%20It%20has%20sought%20to%20articulate%20their%20anguish%20and%20distress%20and%20to%20highlight%20the%20role%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements%20of%20all%20hues%20fighting%20for%20social%20justice.%20It%20has%20also%20carried%20reports%20that%20critically%20analyse%20international%20events%20seen%20through%20the%20often%20differing%20perspectives%20of%20individual%20authors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hounding%20of%20Newsclick%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20granted%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20the%20signatories%20say%2C%20highlighting%20that%20the%20website%20offers%20the%20kind%20of%20information%20that%20is%20necessary%20for%20people%20to%20fight%20the%20injustice%20they%20are%20subjected%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20conscientious%20role%20of%20independent%20journalism%20in%20a%20democracy%20to%20inform%20its%20readers%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failings%20and%20to%20hold%20the%20government%20accountable.%20It%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20right%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20to%20information%20that%20can%20enable%20them%20to%20fight%20against%20injustice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20pushes%20under%20the%20spotlight%20the%20limited%20space%20for%20independent%20journalist.%20It%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20in%20the%20era%20of%20corporate-owned%20media%2C%20the%20space%20for%20independent%20journalism%20that%20is%20free%20of%20corporate%20influence%20has%20shrunk.%20It%20is%20all%20the%20more%20unfortunate%20that%20a%20vicious%20media%20trial%20is%20being%20staged%20although%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations%20brought%20against%20Newsclick%20are%20in%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692186904000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F202