0of%20the%20Azovstal%20steel%20plant%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Mariupol%20last%20year.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20and%20most%20famous%20showdowns%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20role%20made%20him%20a%20particular%20target%2C%20and%20that%20he%20was%20in%20Russian%20captivity%20for%20almost%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20first%20taken%20to%20a%20facility%20in%20occupied%20Ukraine%20and%20then%20moved%20inside%20Russia's%20borders%2C%20to%20the%20city%20of%20Taganrog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20when%20he%20arrived%20a%20Russian%20officer%20told%20him%20and%20other%20Ukrainians%3A%20%26quot%3BHello%20boys.%20Do%20you%20know%20where%20you%20are%3F%20You'll%20rot%20here%20until%20the%20end%20of%20your%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Ukrainian%20captives%20were%20inspected%20twice%20a%20day%2C%20and%20Russian%20guards%20needed%20little%20excuse%20to%20abuse%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BThey%20might%20not%20have%20liked%20how%20you%20left%20the%20cell%2C%20or%20you%20weren't%20quick%20to%20get%20out%2C%20or%20your%20arms%20were%20too%20low%20or%20your%20head%20was%20too%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuards%20during%20a%20check%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20had%20a%20girlfriend%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BGive%20us%20her%20Instagram.%20We'll%20take%20a%20picture%20of%20you%20and%20send%20it%20to%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20beaten%20after%20saying%20she%20didn't%20have%20social%20media%2C%20which%20he%20told%20the%20BBC%20was%20a%20lie.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20basement%20where%20he%20saw%20a%20Ukrainian%20with%20needles%20put%20under%20his%20fingernails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeredniak%20said%20he%20was%20beaten%20with%20a%20wooden%20chair%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%20that%20it%20broke%20in%20parts%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20described%20other%20beatings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20captors%20interrogated%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20actions%20like%20looting%20Mariupol%20and%20ordering%20his%20troops%20to%20kill%20civilians%3A%20%26quot%3BUntil%20you%20said%20what%20they%20were%20interested%20in%2C%20and%20in%20the%20way%20they%20wanted%20to%20hear%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20stop%20beating%20you.%26quot%3B%20He%20did%20not%20say%20if%20he%20ever%20gave%20a%20false%20confession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20human-rights%20group%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20Russia%20used%20apparent%20false%20confessions%20by%20Ukrainians%20against%20them%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhii%20Rotchuk%2C%20also%20from%20the%20Azov%20Regiment%2C%20said%20he%20was%20beaten%20for%20having%20tattoos%2C%20given%20electric%20shocks%2C%20and%20kicked%20in%20the%20chest.%20He%20said%20he%20met%20a%20Ukrainian%20doctor%20who%20falsely%20confessed%20to%20removing%20the%20testicles%20of%20a%20Russian%20prisoner%20because%20he%20was%20beaten%20so%20much%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%3A%20'OK%2C%20just%20leave%20me%20alone%2C%20I%20will%20sign%20the%20confession.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20former%20prisoners%20of%20war%20who%20were%20at%20Taganrog%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20prisoners%20of%20war%20there%20gave%20false%20confessions%20after%20they%20were%20threatened%20and%20intimidated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20told%20the%20BBC%20they%20were%20not%20given%20enough%20food%2C%20inspected%20daily%2C%20beaten%2C%20given%20electric%20shocks%2C%20and%20interrogated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20they%20didn't%20get%20proper%20medical%20help%2C%20and%20the%20BBC%20also%20cited%20reports%20of%20some%20prisoners%20of%20war%20dying%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeredniak%20said%20they%20were%20given%20little%20food%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bif%20I%20ate%20300-400%20calories%20a%20day%2C%20I%20was%20lucky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20defence%20ministry%20previously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fun-experts-raise-widespread-torture-concerns-with-russia-2023-06-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edenied%20im