C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20said%20that%20if%20elected%20he'd%20accept%20China%20seizing%20Taiwan%20once%20the%20US%20secures%20its%20own%20supply%20of%20semiconductors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhughhewitt.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-on-all-things-national-security%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20to%20conservative%20radio%20host%20Hugh%20Hewitt%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ramaswamy%20said%20that%20if%20he%20becomes%20president%20he%20would%20ensure%20that%20the%20US%20is%20no%20longer%20reliant%20on%20Taiwan%20for%20its%20supply%20of%20semiconductors%2C%20a%20crucial%20component%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20goods%20including%20smartphones%20and%20electric%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan%20dominates%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20semiconductors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-would-destroy-taiwan-semiconductor-factories-avoid-china-trump-adviser-2023-3%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Eproducing%20about%2060%25%20of%20the%20world's%20supply.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20also%20said%20that%20if%20the%20US%20could%20show%20it%20was%20serious%20about%20%26quot%3Bsemiconductor%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20securing%20its%20own%20production%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20it%20would%20deter%20Chinese%20aggression%20toward%20Taiwan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20there%20are%20two%20reasons%20why%20China%20wants%20to%20annex%20Taiwan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20is%20to%20squat%20on%20the%20semiconductor%20supply%20chain%20so%20they%20can%20exert%20leverage%20over%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%20That's%20not%20happening%20on%20my%20watch.%20I'd%20take%20a%20firm%20position%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20second%20reason%20why%20is%20that%20they%20have%20unfinished%20nationalistic%20business%20dating%20back%20to%20their%20civil%20war%20in%201949%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20that's%20the%20sole%20basis%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%20going%20after%20Taiwan%20after%20we%20have%20semiconductor%20independence%2C%20then%20you%20know%20what%3F%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20send%20our%20sons%20and%20daughters%20to%20die%20over%20that%20conflict.%20And%20that's%20consistent%20with%20my%20position%20on%20Ukraine%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20said%20that%20he's%20been%20very%20clear%20that%20China's%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20should%20not%20mess%20with%20Taiwan%20until%20after%20the%20US%20has%20achieved%20semiconductor%20independence%2C%20%26quot%3Buntil%20the%20end%20of%20my%20first%20term%20when%20I%20will%20lead%20us%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20after%20that%2C%20our%20commitments%20to%20Taiwan%2C%20our%20commitments%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20go%20to%20military%20conflict%2C%20will%20change%20after%20that%2C%20because%20that's%20rationally%20in%20our%20self-interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20honest.%20That%20is%20true%2C%20and%20that%20is%20credible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20claimed%20sovereignty%20over%20Taiwan%20since%201949%2C%20when%20the%20nationalist%20faction%20in%20the%20Chinese%20civil%20war%20fled%20to%20the%20island%20and%20claimed%20independence%20from%20the%20mainland's%20Communist%20government.%20In%20recent%20years%20tensions%20between%20China%20and%20Taiwan%20have%20intensified%2C%20with%20Xi%20saying%20%26quot%3Breunification%26quot%3B%20with%20Taiwan%20must%20be%20fulfilled%2C%20and%20hinting%20that%20China%20may%20use%20force%20to%20bring%20it%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20long%20maintained%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-us-would-use-military-if-china-attacked-taiwan-2022-5%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Ea%20position%20of%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20ambiguity%26quot%3B%20regarding%20Taiwan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20refusing%20to%20clearly%20state%20whether%20it%20would%20defend%20Taiwan%20if%20attacked.%20But%20last%20year%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20that%20the%20US%20would%20commit%20military%20force%20to%20defending%20Taiwan%2C%20though%20the%20White%20House%20attempted%20to%20downplay%20the%20suggestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20is%20among%20GOP%20candidates%20campaigning%20to%20reduce%20US%20involvement%20abroad%2C%20calling%20for%20the%20US%20to%20cut%20off%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-presidential-hopeful-ramaswamy-says-would-let-china-invade-taiwan-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692183806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc99444ef9f30019f7d84e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-presidential-hopeful-ramaswamy-says-would-let-china-invade-taiwan-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20is%20campaigning%20on%20isolationist%20policies%20and%20is%20questioning%20the%20US'%20alliance%20with%20Taiwan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-presidential-hopeful-ramaswamy-says-would-let-china-invade-taiwan-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Is%20a%20Test%20Bed%20of%20New%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095357%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.01-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20threw%20up%20two%20diverse%20view%20points%20on%20the%20utility%20of%20force%20in%20internal%20security%20situations.%20While%20either%20option%20%E2%80%93%20use%20and%20non-use%