renamed%20as%20Prime%20Ministers'%20Museum%20and%20Library%20Society.%20The%20decision%20to%20rename%20it%20was%20taken%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20Flagstaff%20House%20during%20the%20British%20Raj%2C%20this%20building%20was%20earlier%20used%20as%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20Commander-in-chief%20of%20British%20forces.%20After%20Independence%2C%20it%20became%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Nehru.%20Following%20his%20death%2C%20it%20was%20converted%20to%20a%20library%20and%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20a%20Pradhanmantri%20Sangrahalaya%20was%20set%20up%20on%20the%20premises%20to%20chronical%20achievements%20of%20all%20the%20Prime%20Ministers%2C%20starting%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20This%20museum%20was%20inaugurated%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFrom%20today%2C%20an%20iconic%20institution%20gets%20a%20new%20name.%20The%20world%20renowned%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20becomes%20PMML%E2%80%94Prime%20Ministers'%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr.%20Modi%20possesses%20a%20huge%20bundle%20of%20fears%2C%20complexes%20and%20insecurities%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20our%20first%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1691648313375002980%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20Twitter%20this%20morning%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20today%2C%20an%20iconic%20institution%20gets%20a%20new%20name.%20The%20world%20renowned%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20becomes%20PMML-Prime%20Ministers'%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20insecure%20about%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20had%20a%20single%20point%20agenda%20of%20denying%2C%20distorting%2C%20defaming%20and%20destroying%20Nehru%20and%20the%20Nehruvian%20legacy.%20He%20has%20erased%20N%20and%20put%20P%20instead.%20That%20P%20is%20really%20for%20pettiness%20and%20peeve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20he%20can%20never%20take%20away%20Nehru's%20gigantic%20contributions%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%20his%20towering%20achievements%20in%20building%20the%20democratic%2C%20secular%2C%20scientific%20and%20liberal%20foundations%20of%20the%20Indian%20nation-state%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20now%20under%20assault%20by%20Mr.%20Modi%20and%20his%20drumbeaters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20Nehru's%20%26quot%3Blegacy%20will%20live%20on%20for%20the%20world%20to%20see%20and%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20inspire%20generations%20to%20come%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh's%20remarks%20were%20backed%20by%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20united%20against%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20response%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message%20that%20for%20Mr%20Ramesh%2C%20%26quot%3BP%20means%20only%20Parivar%20(family)%20and%20not%20people%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20jab%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20museum%2C%20a%20library%20which%20would%20showcase%20the%20achievements%20of%20all%20the%20Prime%20Ministers%20of%20this%20country%2C%20from%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20the%20current%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20from%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shashtri%20to%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20to%20HD%20Devegowda%20to%20Inder%20Kumar%20Gujral%20--%20all%20of%20them%20have%20made%20this%20country%20great%20--%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20opposing%20and%20saying%20it%20should%20be%20named%20after%20only%20one%20Prime%20Minister%20from%20one%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Poonawalla%20asked%20if%20Nehru's%20legacy%20was%20so%20weak%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20one%20institution%20is%20named%20after%20all%20Prime%20Ministers%2C%20his%20legacy%20will%20be%20demolished%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20shows%20their%20mindset%20of%20putting%20Parivar%20above%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692181500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Frfee1c3c_nehru-museum-pti_625x300_16_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-museum-jairam-ramesh-bjp-india-pm-narendra-modi-pradhanmantri-sangrahalaya-congress-p-for-petty-jab-as-nehru-museum-renamed-bjps-parivar-reply-4302400%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20renaming%20of%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20(NMML)%20has%20sparked%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20BJP%20and%20opposition%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-museum-jairam-ramesh-bjp-india-pm-narendra-modi-pradhanmantri-sangrahalaya-congress-p-for-petty-jab-as-nehru-museum-renamed-bjps-parivar-reply-4302400%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-museum-jairam-ramesh-bjp-india-pm-narendra-modi-pradhanmantri-sangrahalaya-congress-p-for-petty-jab-as-nehru-museum-renamed-bjps-parivar-reply-4302400%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnehru-museum-jairam-ramesh-bjp-india-pm-narendra-modi-pradhanmantri-sangrahalaya-congress-p-for-petty-jab-as-nehru-museum-renamed-bjps-parivar-reply-4302400%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maui%20fire%3A%20First%20victims%20named%20as%20death%20toll%20reaches%20106%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%