0slumped%20by%203.6%25%20or%20%243%2C198%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWealth%20evolution%20proved%20resilient%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20era%20and%20grew%20at%20a%20record%20pace%20during%202021.%20But%20inflation%2C%20rising%20interest%20rates%20and%20currency%20depreciation%20caused%20a%20reversal%20in%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20outcome%20represents%20a%20break%20in%20the%20almost%20uninterrupted%20expansion%20of%20household%20wealth%20this%20century%2C%20it%20is%20less%20of%20a%20departure%20than%20it%20may%20appear%20at%20first%20sight.%20Further%20examination%20reveals%20that%20wealth%20losses%20are%20heavily%20concentrated%20among%20the%20richer%20nations%20in%20Europe%2C%20North%20America%20and%20Asia-Pacific%2C%20and%20affect%20financial%20assets%20much%20more%20than%20non-financial%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHousehold%20wealth%20got%20a%20boost%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20as%20COVID-19%20relief%20packages%20and%20low%20interest%20rates%20increased%20income%20for%20consumers.%20But%20following%20Russia's%20war%20with%20Ukraine%2C%20global%20inflation%20levels%20surged.%20That's%20sparked%20an%20aggressive%20policy%20reaction%20from%20central%20banks%2C%20which%20have%20hiked%20interest%20rates%20sharply%20over%20the%20past%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmortgage-rates-loan-interest-rates-why-fed-matters-2023-8%5C%22%3Ehas%3C%2Fa%3E%20jacked%20up%20benchmark%20borrowing%20costs%20to%20level%20above%205%25%2C%20from%20near-zero%20levels%20in%20early%202022%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20cool%20historically%20high%20US%20inflation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%20tend%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20consumer%20spending%20power%2C%20eating%20away%20at%20individual%20savings%20and%20wealth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20UBS%2C%20local%20currency%20depreciation%20against%20the%20greenback%20also%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20eroding%20global%20wealth.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdollar-outlook-strength-currency-rally-treasury-markets-investors-fitch-downgrade-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20largely%20strengthened%20since%20the%20Fed%20began%20hiking%20rates%2C%20making%20imports%20more%20expensive%20for%20other%20countries%2C%20and%20weighing%20on%20spending%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobal-wealth-fell-11t-2022-inflation-interest-rates-strong-dollar-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692180878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc8e4b4ef9f30019f7d18e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobal-wealth-fell-11t-2022-inflation-interest-rates-strong-dollar-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Total%20global%20household%20wealth%20dropped%20by%20%2411.3%20trillion%20to%20%24454.4%20trillion%20in%202022%20amid%20runaway%20inflation%20and%20surging%20interest%20rates%2C%20a%20UBS%20study%20showed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ztayeb%40businessinsider.com%20(Zahra%20Tayeb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobal-wealth-fell-11t-2022-inflation-interest-rates-strong-dollar-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%20gets%20Cabinet%20nod%2C%20craftsmen%20to%20get%20subsidised%20loans%20at%205%25%20interest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692180677000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102770145%2Cimgsize-44268.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Floan-to-craftsmen-union-cabinet-pm-modi-vishwakarma-subsidised-loan-vishwakarma-yojana-scheme%2Farticleshow%2F102770095.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20scheme%20will%20be%20launched%20on%20Vishwakarma%20Jayanti%20on%20September%2017.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20days%20to%20come%2C%20we%20will%20launch%20a%20scheme%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Vishwakarma%20Jayanti%2C%20benefiting%20individuals%20skilled%20in%20traditional%20craftsmanship%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Floan-to-craftsmen-union-cabinet-pm-modi-vishwakarma-subsidised-loan-vishwakarma-yojana-scheme%2Farticleshow%2F102770095.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22No%20Such%20Offer%5C%22%3A%20Supriya%20Sule%20Rejects%20Congress%20Claim%20Of%20Central%20Cabinet%20Seat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20a%20media%20report%20of%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%2C%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%2C%20claiming%20that%20a%20central%20cabinet%20berth%20had%20been%20offered%20to%20NCP%20stalwart%20Sharad%20Pawar%20or%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20the%20latter%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20no%20one%20has%20approached%20her%20with%20an%20offer%20of%20a%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20she%20said%20the%20party%20leaders%20should%20introspect%20on%20why%20they%20were%20making%20such%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20reporters%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20received%20no%20such%20offer%20and%20neither%20has%20anyone%20had%20any%20conversations%20on%20those%20lines%20with%20me.%C2%A0You%20should%20ask%20them%20(Maharashtra%20Congress%20leaders)%20why%20they%20are%20giving%20such%20statements.%20I%20have%20no%20idea.%20I%20am%20personally%20in%20touch%20with%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20such%20as%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20but%20I%20am%20not%20in%20touch%20with%20any%20of%20their%20leaders%20in%20Maharashtra.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%2C%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar%2C%20questioned%20the%20recent%20meeting%20between%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20rival%20faction%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20along%20with%208%20loyalist%20MLAs%2C%20engineered%20a%20split%20in%20the%20NCP%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20rival%20faction%20joined%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%20taking%20oath%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Wadettiwar%20claimed%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20put%20forward%20a%20condition%20for%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20be%20made%20the%20Maharashtra%20CM%20%E2%80%94%20that%20he%20has%20to%20convince%20his%20uncle%20to%20join%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20Ajit%20Pawar%20frequently%20meeting%20Sharad%20Pawar%3F%20The%20BJP's%20position%20in%20the%20state%20has%20improved%20even%20after%20they%20engineered%20a%20split%20in%20two%20parties%20(NCP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena).%20Hence%2C%20they%20are%20having%20to%20turn%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar%20as%20he%20is%20a%20mass%20leader.%20Without%20his%20help%2C%20the%20BJP%20won't%20win%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20the%20state%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20reason%20(for%20the%20meetings)%20is%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20told%20Ajit%20Pawar%20that%20he%20cannot%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20unless%20he%20can%20convince%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20come%20on%20board%20(join%20NDA)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wadettiwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20core%20committee%20meeting%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20was%20underway%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Nana%20Patole%20hit%20out%20at%20Deputy%20CM%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20his%20uncle%20over%20the%20secret%20meeting%20held%20at%20Pune%2C%20saying%20that%20such%20meetings%20were%20creating%20confusion%20among%20the%20people.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BSuch%20meetings%20are%20creating%20confusion%20among%20the%20people.%20If%20they%20are%20relatives%2C%20what%20was%20the%20need%20for%20them%20to%20meet%20secretly%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%20himself%2C%20scotched%20speculations%20of%20his%20switch%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20which%20gained%20ground%20following%20his%20meeting%20with%C2%A0Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20secret%20meeting%20as%20was%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20wrong%20with%20me%20meeting%20my%20nephew%3F%20How%20it%20could%20be%20a%20secret%20when%20it%20was%20held%20at%20someone's%20residence%3F%20I%20was%20at%20his%20(Ajit%20Pawar's)%20residence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patole%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20developments%20in%20Maharashtra%20politics%20and%20will%20raise%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20upcoming%20INDIA%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalks%20have%20also%20been%20held%20with%20our%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20this%20regard.%20The%20Congress%20high%20command%20is%20also%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20this.%20The%20matter%20will%20also%20be%20up%20for%20discussion%20during%20the%20INDIA%20meeting%C2%A0in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20united%20Opposition%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20are%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20their%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20over%20two%20days%20%E2%80%94%20August%2031%20and%20September%201%2C%20Congress%20sources%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692180600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2Fdh70i3ug_supriya-sule_625x300_06_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-rejects-congress-claim-of-central-cabinet-seat-have-received-no-such-offer-4302116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reacting%20to%20a%20media%20report%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%2C%20claiming%20that%20a%20central%20cabinet%20berth%20had%20been%20offered%20to%20NCP%20stalwart%20Sharad%20Pawar%20or%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20the%20latter%20said%20no%20one%20has%20approached%20her%20with%20an%20offer%20of%20a%20portfolio.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-rejects-congress-claim-of-central-cabinet-seat-have-received-no-such-offer-4302116%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-rejects-congress-claim-of-central-cabinet-seat-have-received-no-such-offer-4302116%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-rejects-congress-claim-of-central-cabinet-seat-have-received-no-such-offer-4302116%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Good%20Wife%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Eve%20Teasing%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Weakness%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20No-Nos%20in%20SC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Gender%20Stereotype%E2%80%99%20Handbook%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25123828%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_03.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20brought%20out%20a%2030-page%20handbook%20against%20gender%20stereotypes%20so%20that%20judges%20and%20others%20can%20use%20appropriate%20terms%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%20while%20releasing%20the%20book%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cidentifies%20stereotypes%20used%20by%20courts%20and%20how%20they%20are%20unwittingly%20used.%E2%80%9D%20The%20CJI%20stressed%20that%20the%20book%20does%20not%20mean%20to%20criticise%20earlier%20judgments%20but%20should%20help%20judges%20avoid%20it%20by%20%E2%80%9Crecognising%20language%20which%20leads%20to%20stereotypes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20CJI%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-dy-chandrachud-legal-glossary%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20court%20would%20soon%20reveal%20a%20legal%20glossary%20of%20inappropriate%20gendered%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%20handles%20the%20nature%20of%20gender%20stereotyping%20that%20pervades%20judicial%20decision%20making%20and%20the%20necessity%20to%20understand%20them%20and%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20contains%20a%20long%20list%20of%20phrases%20and%20words%20which%20perpetuate%20a%20stereotype%20and%20suggests%20alternative%20language%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20place%20of%20%E2%80%9Cadulteress%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20suggests%20%E2%80%9Cwoman%20who%20has%20engaged%20in%20sexual%20relations%20outside%20of%20marriage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%E2%80%9Caffair%2C%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Crelationship%20outside%20of%20marriage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWords%20like%20%E2%80%9Cconcubine%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cprostitute%E2%80%9D%20are%20to%20be%20replaced%20with%20%E2%80%9Cwoman%20with%20whom%20a%20man%20has%20had%20romantic%20or%20sexual%20relations%20outside%20of%20marriage%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csex%20worker%2C%E2%80%9D%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%20suggests%20just%20using%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cwoman%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20pejorative%20phrases%20and%20words%20like%20%E2%80%9Ccareer%20woman%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Cchaste%20woman%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwoman%20of%20easy%20virtue%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Charlot%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Cwhore%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Cslut%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Cseductress%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwoman%20of%20loose%20morals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Stereotype%20versus%20reality%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20lists%20%E2%80%98stereotype%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98reality%E2%80%99%20against%20each%20other%20to%20illustrate%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20two.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20stereotype%20is%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20overly%20emotional%2C%20illogical%2C%20and%20cannot%20take%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20however%2C%20the%20reality%20listed%20against%20this%20stereotype%20is%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20person%E2%80%99s%20gender%20does%20not%20determine%20or%20influence%20their%20capacity%20for%20rational%20thought.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%2C%20crucially%2C%20cites%20when%20judges%20have%20perpetuated%20such%20stereotypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20the%20stereotype%20that%20%E2%80%9Cunmarried%20women%20(or%20young%20women)%20are%20incapable%20of%20taking%20important%20decisions%20about%20their%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20footnote%20that%20cites%20a%202017%20judgment%20by%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20which%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20girl%20aged%2024%20years%20is%20weak%20and%20vulnerable%2C%20capable%20of%20being%20exploited%20in%20many%20ways.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20reversed%20this%20decision%20in%20%3Cem%3EShafin%20Jahan%20v.%20Asokan%20K.M.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%202018%2C%20the%20handbook%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20High%20Court%20has%20lost%20sight%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20is%20a%20major%2C%20capable%20of%20her%20own%20decisions%20and%20is%20entitled%20to%20the%20right%20recognised%20by%20the%20Constitution%20to%20lead%20her%20life%20exactly%20as%20she%20pleases%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20table%20outlines%20some%20common%20stereotypes%20about%20the%20gender%20roles%20ascribed%20to%20men%20and%20women%2C%20and%20why%20they%20are%20incorrect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20stereotypes%20listed%20is%20one%20that%20courts%20in%20India%20frequently%20deal%20with%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cwives%20should%20take%20care%20of%20their%20husband%E2%80%99s%20parents.%E2%80%9D%20The%20handbook%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20responsibility%20of%20taking%20care%20of%20elderly%20individuals%20in%20the%20family%20falls%20equally%20on%20individuals%20of%20all%20genders.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20sole%20remit%20of%20women.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20stereotypes%20in%20sexual%20violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%2C%20most%20significantly%2C%20devotes%20quite%20a%20few%20pages%20to%20stereotypes%20that%20are%20often%20applied%20to%20men%20and%20women%20in%20the%20context%20of%20sex%20and%20sexual%20violence%20and%20explains%20why%20such%20assumptions%20are%20wrong.%20It%20handles%20how%20courts%20have%20opined%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20when%20they%20have%20been%20victims%20of%20sexual%20crimes%20and%20also%20the%20question%20of%20caste%20atrocities%20in%20this%20regard.%20Some%20examples%20from%20that%20section%20are%20cited%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EStereotype%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EReality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EWomen%20who%20dress%20in%20clothes%20that%20are%20not%20considered%20to%20be%20traditional%20want%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20relations%20with%20men.%20If%20a%20man%20touches%20such%20a%20woman%20without%20her%20consent%2C%20it%20is%20her%20fault.%20The%20clothing%20or%20attire%20of%20a%20woman%20neither%20indicates%20that%20she%20wishes%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20relations%20nor%20is%20it%20an%20invitation%20to%20touch%20her.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EWomen%20are%20capable%20of%20verbally%20communicating%20with%20others%20and%20their%20choice%20of%20clothing%20represents%20a%20form%20of%20self-expression%20that%20is%20independent%20of%20questions%20of%20sexual%20relations.%20A%20man%20who%20touches%20a%20woman%20without%20her%20consent%20must%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20take%20the%20defence%20that%20the%20woman%20invited%20his%20touch%20by%20dressing%20in%20a%20particular%20way.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EWomen%20who%20consume%20alcohol%20or%20smoke%20cigarettes%20want%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20relations%20with%20men.%20If%20a%20man%20touches%20such%20a%20woman%20without%20her%20consent%2C%20it%20is%20her%20fault.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EWomen%2C%20like%20all%20other%20people%2C%20may%20consume%20alcohol%3Cbr%3E%5Cnor%20smoke%20cigarettes%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20including%3Cbr%3E%5Cnfor%20recreation.%20The%20consumption%20of%20alcohol%20or%20use%20of%3Cbr%3E%5Cntobacco%20is%20not%20an%20indication%20of%20their%20desire%20for%20sexual%3Cbr%3E%5Cnrelations%20with%20a%20man.%20A%20man%20who%20touches%20a%20woman%3Cbr%3E%5Cnwithout%20her%20consent%20must%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20take%20the%3Cbr%3E%5Cndefence%20that%20the%20woman%20invited%20his%20touch%20by%20drinking%3Cbr%3E%5Cnor%20smoking.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EWomen%20who%20are%20sexually%20assaulted%20or%20raped%20by%20men%20complain%20about%20the%20injustice%20immediately.%20If%20they%20complain%20after%20a%20time%2C%20they%20are%20lying.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EIt%20takes%20courage%20and%20strength%20to%20report%20a%20sexual%20offence%20because%20of%20the%20stigma%20attached%20to%20them.%20The%20stigma%20attached%20to%20sexual%20violence%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20women%20to%20disclose%20the%20incident%20to%20others.%20Women%20may%20therefore%20register%20a%20complaint%20after%20a%20lapse%20of%20some%20time%2C%20when%20she%20thinks%20she%20is%20able%20to.%20Further%2C%20as%20noted%20above%2C%20several%20other%20factors%20such%20as%20lack%20of%20familial%20support%20or%20fear%20of%20repercussions%20may%20cause%20a%20survivor%20%2F%20victim%20to%20delay%20their%20reporting.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EDominant%20caste%20men%20do%20not%20want%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20relations%20with%20women%20from%20oppressed%20castes.%20Therefore%2C%20any%20allegation%20of%20sexual%20assault%20or%20rape%20by%20an%20oppressed%20caste%20woman%20against%20a%20dominant%20caste%20man%20is%20false.%20Rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%20have%20long%20been%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20social%20control.%20Dominant%20caste%20men%20have%20historically%20used%20sexual%20violence%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20reinforce%20and%20maintain%20caste%20hierarchies.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3ERape%20and%20sexual%20violence%20have%20long%20been%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20social%20control.%20Dominant%20caste%20men%20have%20historically%20used%20sexual%20violence%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20reinforce%20and%20maintain%20caste%20hierarchies.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EA%20woman%20who%20has%20previously%20had%20sexual%20relations%20cannot%20be%20raped%20because%20she%20has%20%E2%80%9Cloose%20morals%E2%80%9D%20or%20a%20%E2%80%9Cloose%20character.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EA%20woman%20who%20consents%20to%20sexual%20activity%20with%20one%20man%20does%20not%20consent%20to%20sexual%20activity%20with%20all%20men.%20Similarly%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20consents%20to%20sexual%20activity%20with%20a%20man%20at%20a%20particular%20instance%20does%20not%20ipso%20facto%20consent%20to%20sexual%20activity%20with%20that%20same%20man%20at%20all%20other%20instances.%20A%20woman%E2%80%99s%20character%20or%20morals%20are%20unrelated%20to%20the%20number%20of%20sexual%20partners%20she%20has%20had.%20Her%20sexual%20history%20does%20not%20define%20her%20and%20must%20not%20influence%20criminal%20proceedings.%20Section%2053A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%201872%20attempts%20to%20combat%20this%20very%20stereotype%20by%20prohibiting%20lawyers%20from%20adducing%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20of%20the%20character%20of%20the%20survivor%20%2F%20victim%20or%20of%20such%20person%E2%80%99s%20previous%20sexual%20experience%E2%80%9D%20where%20the%20question%20of%20consent%20is%20in%20issue.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20section%20also%20deals%20with%20and%20debunks%20topical%20stereotypes%20like%20%E2%80%9Cmen%20are%20unable%20to%20control%20their%20sexual%20desires%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20a%20man%20to%20rape%20a%20sex%20worker%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Ctransgender%20individuals%20cannot%20be%20raped%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20behave%20differently%20from%20Western%20women%20or%20women%20of%20other%20countries%20after%20a%20man%20has%20sexually%20assaulted%20or%20raped%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20in%20this%20section%20and%20later%2C%20the%20handbook%20stresses%20that%20delay%20in%20filing%20an%20FIR%20or%20complaint%20cannot%20be%20mechanically%20used%20to%20create%3Cbr%3E%5Cndoubt%20in%20a%20case%20of%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20offender%20could%20be%20an%20employer%2C%20neighbour%2C%20family%20member%2C%20or%20friend%20creating%20several%20complications%20in%20immediately%20reporting%20an%20instance%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20book%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%20notes%20that%20women%20have%20historically%20faced%20numerous%20prejudiced%20beliefs%20and%20stereotypes%20which%20have%20impeded%20their%20access%20to%20fair%20and%20equal%20treatment%20within%20society%20and%20the%20justice%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20judiciary%20must%20recognise%20the%20deep-rooted%20impact%20of%20gender%20stereotypes%20and%20actively%20work%20to%20dismantle%20them%20from%20its%20thinking%2C%20decision-making%2C%20and%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says%2C%20advocating%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20language%20to%20combat%20harmful%20patterns%20of%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20before%2C%20this%20glossary%20has%20been%20prepared%20by%20a%20committee%20chaired%20by%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Moushumi%20Bhattacharya.%20Others%20involved%20in%20this%20included%20former%20judges%2C%20Justice%20Prabha%20Sridevan%20and%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal.%20Also%2C%20Professor%20Jhuma%20Sen%20who%20is%20currently%20an%20adjunct%20faculty%20member%20at%20the%20West%20Bengal%20National%20University%20of%20Juridical%20Sciences%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20in%20September%2C%20in%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20move%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20gazette%20published%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Forinam.net%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2FTN_gazette_glossary_2022.pdf%5C%22%3Ea%20glossary%20of%20LGBTQIA%2B%20terms%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20deepen%20sensitisation%20over%20other%20aspects%20of%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692180523000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25123828%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_03.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-gender-stereotype-handbook%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20other%20things%2C%20this%20handbook%20devotes%20quite%20a%20few%20pages%20to%20stereotypes%20that%20are%20often%20applied%20to%20men%20and%20women%20in%20the%20context%20of%20sex%20and%20sexu