man%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Fabhishek-bachchan-saiyami-kher-cricket-disability-ghoomer-1235696619%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Fabhishek-bachchan-saiyami-kher-cricket-disability-ghoomer-1235696619%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Fabhishek-bachchan-saiyami-kher-cricket-disability-ghoomer-1235696619%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20Find%20'Demon%20Particle'%2C%20Nearly%2070%20Years%20After%20It%20Was%20Predicted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20discovered%20a%20remarkable%20'demon%20particle'%20that%20holds%20the%20potential%20to%20usher%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20superconductors%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20by%20researchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign.%20The%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-023-06318-8%5C%22%3Ejournal%20%3Cem%3ENature%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20detailed%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20particle%20and%20was%20first%20predicted%20nearly%2070%20years%20ago%20by%20physicist%20David%20Pines.%20A%20superconductor%2C%20a%20special%20type%20of%20metal%20or%20alloy%2C%20possesses%20the%20remarkable%20ability%20to%20transmit%20electrical%20currents%20without%20any%20hindrance.%20However%2C%20current%20superconductors%20require%20the%20temperature%20to%20fall%20below%20100%20degrees%20Fahrenheit-mark%20to%20maintain%20their%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20advancements%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20have%20led%20to%20the%20identification%20of%20a%20transparent%2C%20massless%2C%20and%20neutral%20particle%2C%20indicating%20its%20capacity%20to%20manifest%20regardless%20of%20temperature%2C%20within%20the%20metal%20strontium%20ruthenate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20superconductors%20already%20find%20use%20in%20applications%20such%20as%20maglev%20trains%20and%20precision-enhancing%20magnetic%20resonance%20imaging%20(MRI)%20apparatus%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20materials%20that%20can%20perform%20this%20feat%20at%20room%20temperature%20could%20revolutionise%20the%20landscape%2C%20opening%20doors%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20more%20potent%20computing%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPines'%20demon%20is%20a%20plasmon%20-%20that%20behaves%20like%20a%20particle%20-%20meaning%20it's%20a%20quasiparticle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20experiments%20are%20done%20with%20light%20and%20measure%20optical%20properties%2C%20but%20being%20electrically%20neutral%20means%20that%20demons%20don't%20interact%20with%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peter%20Abbamonte%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20physics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign%20and%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20study%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20completely%20different%20kind%20of%20experiment%20was%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20said%20that%20it%20chose%20strontium%20ruthenate%20(Sr2RuO4)%20because%20it%20is%20similar%20to%20high-temperature%20superconductors%20and%20yet%20isn't%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20first%2C%20we%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20was.%20Demons%20are%20not%20in%20the%20mainstream.%20The%20possibility%20came%20up%20early%20on%2C%20and%20we%20basically%20laughed%20it%20off.%20But%2C%20as%20we%20started%20ruling%20things%20out%2C%20we%20started%20to%20suspect%20that%20we%20had%20really%20found%20the%20demon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20graduate%20student%20Ali%20Husain%2C%20a%20co-author%20of%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20added%20that%20further%20research%20is%20needed%20using%20alternative%20methods%20of%20observation%20in%20order%20to%20fully%20understand%20how%20the%20quasiparticle%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692179280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fp8dmej84_nanoparticles-generic-unsplash-650_625x300_07_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-discover-demon-particle-nearly-70-years-after-it-was-predicted-4302278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20transparent%2C%20massless%2C%20and%20neutral%20particle%2C%20with%20the%20capacity%20to%20manifest%20regardless%20of%20temperature%2C%20making%20it%20useful%20for%20superconductors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-discover-demon-particle-nearly-70-years-after-it-was-predicted-4302278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-discover-demon-particle-nearly-70-years-after-it-was-predicted-4302278%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fscientists-discover-demon-particle-nearly-70-years-after-it-was-predicted-4302278%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ben%20Stokes%20comes%20out%20of%20ODI%20retirement%20ahead%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692178847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102769611%2Cimgsize-38354.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fben-stokes-comes-out-of-odi-retirement-ahead-of-the-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F102769500.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirteen%20months%20ago%2C%20Stokes%2C%20who%20is%20also%20England's%20Test%20captain%2C%20stepped%20away%20from%20the%20ODI%20format%20due%20to%20the%20taxing%20demands%20of%20being%20a%20multi-format%20player%2C%20coupled%20with%20concerns%20about%20a%20persistent%20left%20knee%20injury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcrick