ry%2Fnews%2Faerospace-major-boeing-starts-production-of-indian-army-s-apache-choppers-123081600342_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Faerospace-major-boeing-starts-production-of-indian-army-s-apache-choppers-123081600342_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Faerospace-major-boeing-starts-production-of-indian-army-s-apache-choppers-123081600342_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20%5C%22Concubine%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22Ladylike%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22Dutiful%20Wife%5C%22%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20New%20Handbook%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProstitute%2C%20hooker%2C%20whore%2C%20keep%2C%20mistress%2C%20slut%20--%20these%20are%20among%2040-odd%20words%20red-flagged%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20latest%20handbook%20to%20sensitise%20judges%20against%20inadvertently%20furthering%20gender%20biases%20by%20using%20stereotypical%20words%20in%20court%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20launched%20the%20'Handbook%20On%20Combating%20Gender%20Stereotypes'%20this%20morning.%20Flagging%20stereotypical%20words%20used%20in%20past%20court%20judgments%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20words%20are%20improper%20and%20have%20been%20used%20for%20women%20in%20court%20judgments.%20This%20handbook's%20objective%20is%20not%20to%20criticise%20those%20judgments%20or%20doubt%20them.%20This%20is%20just%20to%20underline%20how%20gender%20stereotypes%20are%20perpetuated%20inadvertently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20stereotypes%20may%20impact%20judicial%20decision-making%2C%20the%20handbook%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BLike%20any%20person%2C%20a%20judge%20may%20also%20unconsciously%20hold%20or%20rely%20on%20stereotypes.%20If%20a%20judge%20relies%20on%20preconceived%20assumptions%20about%20people%20or%20groups%20when%20deciding%20cases%20or%20writing%20judgements%2C%20the%20harm%20caused%20can%20be%20enormous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20judges%20reach%20legally%20correct%20outcomes%2C%20the%20use%20of%20reasoning%20or%20language%20that%20promotes%20gender%20stereotypes%20undermines%20the%20unique%20characteristics%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20individuals%20before%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stated%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20stereotypes%20by%20judges%20also%20has%20the%20effect%20of%20entrenching%20and%20perpetuating%20stereotypes%2C%20creating%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20injustice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20several%20stereotypical%20words%20and%20their%20alternatives%2C%20the%20handbook%20stated%20that%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bfaggot%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfallen%20woman%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bharlot%26quot%3B%20need%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with%20in%20court%20judgments.%20Instead%2C%20it%20said%2C%20judges%20should%20accurately%20describe%20the%20sexual%20orientation%20of%20the%20person%20concerned%20--%20homosexual%20or%20bisexual%2C%20use%20%26quot%3Bwoman%26quot%3B%20and%20avoid%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bfallen%20woman%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bharlot%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%220hvleboo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F0hvleboo_supreme-court_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bdutiful%20wife%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bobedient%20wife%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20avoided%2C%20the%20handbook%20stated.%20The%20use%20of%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bravished%26quot%3B%20in%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20or%20rape%20was%20also%20red-flagged%20in%20the%20handbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%20also%20busted%20several%20stereotypes%20attached%20to%20women%2C%20such%20as%20women%20being%20overly%20emotional%20and%20indecisive%2C%20unmarried%20women%20being%20incapable%20of%20taking%20decisions%20and%20all%20women%20wanting%20to%20have%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20glossary%20aims%20to%20help%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20identify%20and%20mitigate%20the%20use%20of%20stereotypes%20and%20stereotype-enforcing%20language%20against%20women%20in%20their%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20states%20the%20handbook%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692178020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-no-concubine-ladylike-dutiful-wife-supreme-courts-new-handbook-4302063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prostitute%2C%20hooker%2C%20whore%2C%20keep%2C%20mistress%2C%20slut%20--%20these%20are%20among%2040-odd%20words%20red-flagged%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20latest%20handbook%20to%20sensitise%20judges%20against%20inadvertently%20furthering%20gender%20biases%20by%20using%20stereotypical%20words%20in%20court%20judgments%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-no-concubine-ladylike-dutiful-wife-supreme-courts-new-handbook-4302063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-no-concubine-ladylike-dutiful-wife-supreme-courts-new-handbook-4302063%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-no-concubine-ladylike-dutiful-wife-supreme-courts-new-handbook-4302063%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Now%2C%20Burger%20King%20says%20tomatoes%20on%20'vacation'%20in%20India%22%2C%22