hile-performing-heres-what-he-did-next-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F102764975.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Why%20Wasn't%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20Brought%20to%20Supreme%20Court%3F'%3A%20Three%20Noted%20Legal%20Minds%20Ask%20SC%20Collegium%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F28192720%2FScreen-Shot-2020-02-28-at-7.27.03-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20retired%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20two%20other%20legal%20luminaries%20have%20together%20written%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fa-question-for-supreme-court-8894242%2F%5C%22%3E%20opinion%20piece%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20asking%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20collegium%20why%20it%20%E2%80%9Crefused%20to%20bring%20Justice%20S.%20Muralidhar%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20apex%20court%20despite%20his%20exemplary%20record%20as%20a%20judge%20and%20legal%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20essay%2C%20headlined%20%E2%80%98A%20question%20for%20the%20collegium%E2%80%99%2C%20appeared%20in%20the%20paper%20today%2C%20August%2016.%20It%20is%20written%20by%20Justice%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%2C%20who%20retired%20as%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20and%20had%20once%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SC%20collegium%20which%20selects%20judges%20for%20appointment%20to%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20noted%20jurist%20and%20senior%20advocate%20Fali%20Nariman%20and%20senior%20advocate%20and%20mediation%20specialist%20Sriram%20Panchu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Muralidhar%20retired%20as%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Orissa%20high%20court%20on%20August%207%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20this%20piece%20is%20to%20ask%20the%20collegium%20why%20his%20retirement%20date%20was%20not%20August%207%2C%202026%2C%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20essay%20opens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20cite%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20years%20as%20a%20lawyer%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20including%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20when%20T.N.%20Seshan%20headed%20it.%20The%20authors%20observed%20that%20his%20engagement%20with%20the%20law%20has%20been%20wide%20and%20deep.%20They%20note%20that%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3ELaw%2C%20Poverty%20and%20Legal%20Aid%3A%20Access%20to%20Criminal%20Justice%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20seminal%20contribution%20to%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20an%20impressive%20bio%20acquired%20%E2%80%9Clegendary%20proportions%2C%E2%80%9D%20write%20the%20authors%2C%20once%20the%20judge%20came%20to%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court.%20He%20served%20there%20between%202006%20and%202020.%20The%20authors%20note%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20many%20significant%20cases%20and%20the%20balance%20he%20struck%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-muralidhar-farewell-speech-full%5C%22%3EJustice%20Muralidhar%20on%20the%20Distinction%20Between%20Neutrality%20and%20Impartiality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20key%20judgements%20that%20Justice%20Muralidhar%20authored%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3ENaz%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFoundation%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20that%20decriminalised%20consensual%20homosexuality%2C%20the%20conviction%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20for%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%2C%20the%20sentencing%20of%2016%20policemen%20for%20the%20killings%20of%2038%20Muslims%20in%20Hashimpura%20and%20the%20bail%20to%20Gautam%20Navlakha%2C%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20note%20especially%20how%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20him%20ensured%20ambulance%20services%20to%20riot-affected%20areas%20in%20northeast%20Delhi%20in%202020%2C%20through%20a%20late%20night%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20appointment%20as%20Orissa%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20the%20writers%20say%2C%20changed%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20hitherto%20quiet%20court%20which%20henceforth%20saw%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20have%20a%20glance%20at%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Orissa%20High%20Court.%20Its%20filings%2C%20records%2C%20fees%20are%20in%20e-mode%2C%20it%20has%20paperless%20benches%2C%20hybrid%20hearings%20and%20e-libraries%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20his%20efforts%20to%20design%20a%20better%20system%20came%20with%20significant%20judicial%20work%20pressure.%20The%20authors%20write%20that%20Justice%20Muralidhar%E2%80%99s%20bench%20disposed%20of%2033%2C322%20cases%20in%20his%2031%20months%20and%20delivered%20545%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guard%20of%20honour%20he%20received%20at%20his%20retirement%20was%20enormous%20and%20%E2%80%9Chas%20never%20happened%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20noted%2C%20observing%20that%20the%20judge%20at%2062%20had%20much%20more%20to%20give%20that%20the%20judiciary%20has%20lost%20a%20treasured%20asset%20with%20his%20retirement.%20Hard%20questions%20must%20thus%20be%20asked%20of%20the%20collegium%2C%20they%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FlVxqEaOZGhI%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22This%20Judge%20Was%20So%20Outstanding%20Modi%20Ensured%20He%20Never%20Made%20It%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20such%20merit%20on%20display%2C%20along%20with%20matchless%20integrity%20and%20probity%2C%20on%20what%20grounds%20was%20he%20denied%20his%20rightful%20place%3F%20Sometimes%20these%20questions%20are%20asked%20rhetorically%2C%20but%20his%20case%20is%20a%20cause%20celebre%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20case%20that%20comes%20up%20to%20illustrate%20the%20workings%20of%20a%20system%2C%20which%20must%20be%20seized%20upon%20if%20we%20want