n%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide%20to%20better%20their%20condition.%20It%20also%20documents%20certain%20red%20flags%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20peace%2C%20including%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20keep%20faith%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20even%20while%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20demand%20his%20removal%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20failing%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20report%20by%20the%20four%20women%20is%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Gains%3F%20Who%20Loses%3F%3A%20Interim%20Reflections%20from%20Manipur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBy%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EDr.%20Syeda%20Hameed%3A%20Mentor%20%E2%80%93%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%2C%20Founder%20member%20South%20Asians%20For%20Human%20Rights.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EDr.%20Roshmi%20Goswami%3A%20National%20Council%20Member%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%2C%20Co-Chair%20South%20Asians%20For%20Human%20Rights%2C%20Co-founder%2C%20North%20East%20Network.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EJarjum%20G%20Ete%3A%20President%20Emeritus%2C%20All%20India%20Union%20of%20Forest%20Working%20People%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EAngela%20Rangad%3A%20TUR%20%E2%80%93%20Thma%20U%20Rangli%20Juki%2C%20KAM%20Meghalaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWAS%20IT%20THE%20RIGHT%20TIME%20TO%20VISIT%20MANIPUR%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20a%20team%20of%20four%20women%20from%20different%20places%20and%20having%20different%20affiliations.%20Three%20of%20us%20from%20the%20North%20East%20and%20one%20from%20Delhi%2C%20having%20different%20ethnicities%20and%20four%20different%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20Christian%2C%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Indigenous%20tribal%20faith.%20For%20one%20of%20us%20the%20process%20of%20connecting%20with%20Manipur%20during%20this%20moment%20of%20unprecedented%20crisis%20had%20already%20begun%20by%20way%20of%20a%20three%20day%20closed%20door%20meeting%20in%20a%20very%20private%20enabling%20feminist%20space%20where%20women%20from%20five%20different%20communities%20of%20Manipur%20were%20able%20to%20come%20together%20to%20talk.%20This%20visit%20came%20about%20from%20that%20closed%20door%20meeting%20and%20was%20initially%20planned%20as%20a%20Goodwill%20visit.%20But%20as%20we%20traveled%20through%20battle%20ravaged%20Manipur%20the%20objective%20of%20our%20visit%20kept%20evolving%2C%20incorporating%20new%20perspectives%20and%20taking%20different%20directions.%20Eventually%20it%20was%20just%20a%20%E2%80%98mission%20of%20listening%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20first%20in%20a%20series%20of%20proposed%20visits%20that%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20undertake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM-300x182.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112704%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.26.18-AM-1024x621.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668279%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20landed%20in%20Imphal%20on%20the%203rd%20of%20August.%20A%20most%20contentious%20day%20to%20arrive%20as%20it%20marked%20three%20months%20since%20the%20fateful%20day%20of%20May%203rd%2C%20and%20the%20Kuki%20community%20had%20proposed%20to%20hold%20a%20mass%20burial%20programme%20of%20their%20dead%20on%20that%20day.%20The%20proposal%20was%20to%20bury%2035%20dead%20including%203%20women%20lying%20in%20the%20Churachandpur%20district%20hospital%20morgue%20at%20S.%20Boljang%20village.%20The%20proposed%20burial%20was%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20a%20hugely%20controversial%20and%20charged%20event%20as%20the%20proposed%20burial%20grounds%20were%20being%20claimed%20by%20both%20sides%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20Kukis%20primarily%20led%20by%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20ITLF%20and%20by%20the%20Coordination%20Committee%20For%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%20for%20the%20Meiteis.%20Mass%20condolence%20ceremonies%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20deceased%20were%20conducted%20at%20the%20peace%20ground%20at%20Turbong%20and%20in%20other%20Kuki%20areas%20and%20were%20already%20over%20by%20the%20time%20we%20reached%20our%20destination%2C%20and%20the%20burial%20was%20however%20deferred%20for%20another%20week%20by%20the%20Manipur%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20asked%20both%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20to%20maintain%20status%20quo%20and%20to%20arrive%20at%20an%20amicable%20settlement%20during%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20this%20flashpoint%20of%20fresh%20confrontation%2C%20the%20entire%20period%20of%20our%20visit%20was%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%98flare%20up%E2%80%99%20period%20which%20was%20highly%20charged%2C%20each%20day%20bringing%20new%20challenges%20of%20heightened%20aggressive%20and%20combat%20posturing%20by%20all%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20groups%2C%20Meira%20Paibis%2C%20Armed%20volunteers%2C%20State%20and%20Central%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20Military.%20We%20were%20therefore%20literally%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20%E2%80%98events%20and%20incidents%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20a%20lived%20experience%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Manipur%20battleground%E2%80%99.%20This%20also%20determined%20where%20we%20could%20go%20and%20where%20we%20could%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20arrival%20at%20Imphal%2C%20we%20met%20a%20cross%20section%20of%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20people%20%E2%80%93%20old%20friends%20who%20we%20had%20journeyed%20together%20with%20in%20earlier%20struggles%20and%20movements%20as%20well%20as%20new%20acquaintances.%20The%20conversations%20that%20evening%20were%20very%20open%20and%20trusting%20and%20provided%20some%20context%20as%20well%20as%20questions.%20We%20were%20to%20visit%20Churachandpur%20or%20as%20some%20like%20to%20call%20it%20today%20Lamka%2C%20the%20very%20next%20day%20after%20our%20arrival.%20But%20after%20the%20tensions%20of%203rd%20August%2C%20we%20were%20advised%20to%20visit%20Tengnoupal%20%E2%80%93%20another%20Kuki%20stronghold%20District%20instead.%20An%20important%20District%20that%20has%20the%20Asian%20highway%20connecting%20Moreh%2C%20here%20we%20witnessed%20the%20massive%20community%20mobilisation%20particularly%20of%20women%20not%20only%20to%20support%20and%20run%20Relief%20camps%20but%20also%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20resistance%20%2F%20defense%20efforts.%20Next%20day%2C%20the%204th%20of%20August%20we%20decided%20to%20leave%20Imphal%20at%20the%20crack%20of%20dawn%20to%20head%20for%20Churachandpur%2C%20only%20for%20us%20to%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20events%20of%20yet%20another%20volatile%20day%20this%20conflict%20had%20seen.%20After%20having%20managed%20to%20negotiate%20our%20way%20through%20several%20Meira%20Paibi%20barricades%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20border%20village%20of%20Kwakta%2C%20when%20our%20Pangal%20(Meitei%20Muslim)%20driver%20flatly%20refused%20to%20go%20any%20further%20after%20we%20had%20cleared%20every%20other%20hurdle.%20The%20incessant%20shelling%20and%20sniping%20from%20the%20surrounding%20hills%20unnerved%20him.%20It%20was%20the%20morning%20when%20three%20people%20had%20just%20been%20killed%20at%203%20am%20while%20still%20sleeping%2C%20and%20the%20bodies%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20retrieved.%20Meira%20Paibis%20from%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Bishnupur%20district%20and%20armed%20volunteers%20were%20pouring%20in%20to%20join%20the%20mourning%20family%20members%20and%20were%20also%20readying%20themselves%20to%20protest%2Fretaliate.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20charged%20situation%2C%20and%20yet%20we%20might%20have%20taken%20a%20chance%20and%20walked%20through%20no%20man%E2%80%99s%20land%20across%20what%20everyone%20there%20describes%20as%20the%20LOC%2C%20where%20our%20Kuki%20friends%20were%20waiting%20to%20receive%20us%2C%20but%20there%20were%20people%20with%20limitations%20in%20our%20team%20and%20we%20had%20to%20be%20mindful.%20Our%20return%20journey%20across%20Imphal%20towards%20our%20hotel%20was%20also%20fraught%20with%20tension%20as%20the%20anger%20and%20anguish%20about%20the%20deaths%20that%20day%20was%20palpable%20when%20we%20were%20stopped%20at%20every%20crossing%20by%20groups%20of%20people%2C%20mainly%20women%20who%20demanded%20to%20see%20our%20IDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20journey%20to%20Kangpokpi%20the%20next%20day%20was%20relatively%20easier%20and%20smoother%2C%20but%20what%20we%20heard%20and%20saw%20there%20left%20us%20heartbroken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20short%20visit%20we%20interacted%20and%20had%20wide%20ranging%20discussions%20with%20a%20cross%20section%20of%20people%20(Meitei%2C%20Kuki%20Zo%20as%20well%20as%20Naga).%20We%20met%20organizations%2C%20women%20and%20student%20leaders%2C%20concerned%20individuals%2C%20experts%20from%20human%20rights%20and%20environmental%20movements%2C%20peace%20activists%20and%20negotiators%2C%20journalists%2C%20researchers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20writers%20and%20theater%20personalities%2C%20students%2C%20relief%20providers%2C%20church%20workers%20and%20others.%20We%20also%20met%20survivors%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20assault%20and%20killings%2C%20families%20of%20disappeared%20peoples%2C%20displaced%20people%20and%20individual%20voices%20against%20the%20drug%20cartel.%20There%20were%20several%20narratives%20%E2%80%93%20some%20more%20dominant%20than%20others%20and%20also%20constantly%20changing%20as%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EANGUISHED%20NARRATIVES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20striking%20expression%20cutting%20across%20both%20the%20Kukis%20and%20Meitei%20people%20we%20interacted%20with%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20situation%2C%20was%20their%20unequivocal%20assertion%20that%20the%20present%20regime%20both%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state%20are%20clearly%20and%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20continued%20violence%20and%20complete%20anarchy%20in%20the%20state.%20People%20were%20unanimous%20in%20saying%20that%20if%20the%20violence%20was%20controlled%20and%20reined%20in%20in%20the%20first%20few%20days%20of%20its%20outburst%20in%20May%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20accelerated%20the%20way%20it%20did%20and%20they%20would%20not%20be%20in%20the%20present%20state%20that%20they%20are%20in.%20They%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20many%20of%20the%20sexual%20violations%20and%20killings%20that%20happened%20after%20the%203rd%20and%204th%20of%20May%20could%20perhaps%20have%20been%20avoided.%20The%20issue%20of%20command%20responsibility%20and%20state%20accountability%20rang%20loud%20and%20clear%20from%20every%20quarter%20and%20category%20of%20people.%20In%20Kwakta%20when%20we%20knelt%20down%20to%20pay%20our%20condolences%20to%20the%20grief%20stricken%20widow%20of%20Prem%20Kumar%20Yumnam%20who%20was%20brutally%20killed%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20earlier%2C%20she%20screamed%20out%20-%E2%80%98%20If%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20controlled%20this%20violence%20three%20months%20ago%20my%20husband%20would%20be%20alive%20today.%20Why%20is%20he%20still%20silent%3F%E2%80%99%20Both%20sides%20believe%20that%20the%20violence%20and%20aggression%20has%20been%20deliberately%20left%20to%20fester%20and%20as%20new%20elements%20are%20added%20the%20situation%20gets%20aggravated%20every%20single%20day.%20The%20Manipur%20crisis%20is%20therefore%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20both%20the%20culpability%20and%20incapability%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20led%20by%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20petulant%20and%20arrogant%20silence%20and%20lack%20of%20empathy%20for%20the%20affected%20people%20shows%20a%20complete%20disregard%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20and%20is%20deeply%20insulting%20to%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM.jpg%201198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM-1022x1024.jpg%201022w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16112828%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.27.59-AM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20institutions%20have%20collapsed%20and%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20sense%20of%20state%20inaction%20with%20bodies%20lying%20in%20the%20morgues%20and%20the%20state%20not%20enabling%20a%20process%20of%20identification%20and%20closure%20for%20grieving%20families.%20Instead%2C%20the%20BJP%20regime%20(%20Cf%3A%20Tushar%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20claims)%20is%20seen%20indulging%20in%20its%20typical%20diversionary%20blame%20game%20by%20labeling%20the%20unclaimed%20bodies%20as%20those%20belonging%20to%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20while%20families%20wait%20in%20anguish%20and%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20were%20also%20raised%20about%20undertrials%20in%20the%20jails%20in%20Imphal%20and%20other%20Meitei%20dominated%20districts%2C%20with%20Kukis%20having%20no%20access%20to%20their%20loved%20ones%20and%20of%20not%20even%20knowing%20if%20they%20are%20still%20alive.%20As%20one%20person%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%20state%20has%20been%20%E2%80%98strategically%20absent%E2%80%99.%20This%20strategic%20absence%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20the%20DNA%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20when%20they%20are%20unable%20or%20unwilling%20to%20take%20action%20either%20because%20of%20incapability%20or%20calculations%20around%20some%20electoral%20gains%20or%20losses.%20People%20simply%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20absence%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20culpability%20was%20particularly%20glaring%20in%20the%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20the%20Kuki%20Zo%20community.%20While%20we%20had%20read%20about%20the%20extent%20and%20depth%20of%20the%20violations%20that%20had%20taken%20place%20since%20May%203%2C%20the%20first%20hand%20accounts%20of%20brutality%20and%20mayhem%20was%20extremely%20shocking%2C%20especially%20accounts%20of%20the%20sexual%20violence%20and%20the%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20any%20norms%20of%20humanity.%20Serious%20doubts%20were%20also%20raised%20about%20the%20partisan%20and%20communal%20role%20played%20by%20higher%20ups%20in%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20narrative%20is%20that%20the%20core%20issue%20is%20not%20even%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20separate%20Kuki%20administration%20or%20clash%20with%20militants%20in%20different%20locations%20but%20that%20it%20is%20essentially%20a%20geo-political%20conflict%20driven%20by%20people%20with%20a%20deep%20rooted%20political%20agenda.%20The%20%E2%80%98strategic%20absence%E2%80%99%20and%20silence%20of%20the%20Centre%20seems%20to%20lend%20credibility%20to%20this%20narrative.%20Along%20the%20same%20narrative%20a%20question%20that%20was%20raised%20by%20several%20people%20including%20those%20who%20have%20been%20directly%20affected%20is%20%E2%80%9CWho%20gains%3F%E2%80%9D%20from%20allowing%20this%20impasse%20to%20continue%20and%20for%20the%20violence%20to%20fester.%20Is%20this%20lingering%20conflict%20a%20cover%20up%20or%20a%20diversion%20from%20other%20things%20that%20are%20going%20on%3F%20Linkages%20to%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20the%20drug%20cartel%20and%20drug%20money%20being%20used%20for%20electioneering%20was%20made%20by%20several%20people%20%E2%80%93%20some%20alluded%20to%20it%20while%20others%20were%20very%20vocal%20with%20ex%20police%20officer%20Thounaojam%20Brinda%20going%20public%20with%20evidence%20in%20asking%20%E2%80%98Is%20CM%20Biren%20Fighting%20a%20War%20against%20Drugs%20or%20For%20Drugs%3F%E2%80%99%20She%20spoke%20to%20us%20at%20length%20on%20the%20various%20aspects%20and%20operational%20strategies%20of%20the%20drug%20mafia%20and%20the%20inextricable%20nexus%20with%20the%20seats%20of%20power%20and%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20higher%20ups%20of%20all%20the%20communities.%20And%20as%20the%20impasse%20continues%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20realization%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide%20that%20ultimately%20all%20communities%20are%20expendable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20in%20conflict%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20severely%20snapped%20at%20least%20for%20now.%20Colleagues%20and%20friends%20who%20had%20lived%20together%20and%20worked%20together%20still%20maintain%20contact%20but%20the%20strains%20of%20everyday%20strife%20are%20pressing%20down%20and%20here%20and%20there%20fissures%20and%20doubt%20were%20visible.%20Amongst%20the%20women%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20this%20breakdown%20of%20ties%20is%20deeply%20felt.There%20is%20immense%20sadness%2C%20grief%20and%20regret%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20the%20incidences%20of%20barbaric%20violence.%20There%20is%20also%20huge%20rage%20and%20anger.%20It%20is%20very%20early%20yet%20and%20too%20fraught%20to%20talk%20about%20peace.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20need%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20practical%20requirements%20that%20have%20arisen%20and%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20build%20trust%20through%20a%20sense%20of%20urgent%20concerns%20common%20to%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide.%20But%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20is%20for%20a%20cessation%20of%20violence%20and%20hostilities.%20Most%20felt%20that%20this%20was%20possible%20only%20with%20the%20removal%20of%20CM%20Biren%20Singh.%20The%20call%20for%20his%20removal%20came%20from%20both%20the%20communities%20and%20debunked%20the%20narrative%20that%20he%20has%20unanimous%20support%20from%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kukis%20across%20the%20board%20reiterated%20their%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20as%20trust%20has%20been%20broken%20and%20they%20no%20longer%20feel%20safe%20to%20be%20under%20the%20same%20jurisdiction%20as%20the%20Meiteis.%20No%20doubt%20the%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20precedes%20the%20May%203rd%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20but%20since%20then%20and%20whatever%20has%20happened%20during%20this%20three%20month%20period%20strengthens%20the%20demand%20and%20the%20resolve%20of%20the%20Kukis%20to%20be%20separate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20582px)%2085vw%2C%20582px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22582%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM-1024x1021.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113023%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.29.57-AM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668281%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22581%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20visit%20to%20the%20relief%20camps%20and%20our%20conversations%20with%20family%20members%20and%20women%20support%20groups%20of%20the%20disappeared%20and%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20violence%20has%20provided%20practical%20and%20some%20telling%20gendered%20insights%20which%20is%20being%20included%20in%20the%20section%20on%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation.%20The%20meeting%20with%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20getting%20to%20know%20her%20story%20and%20its%20aftermath%20from%20her%20detailed%20FIR%20and%20from%20people%20around%20her%20was%20especially%20painful%20and%20shook%20us%20profoundly.%20Her%20mother%20(a%20person%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20cleaner%20in%20Imphal)%20was%20emphatic%20about%20justice%2C%20seeking%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20the%20perpetrators%20but%20not%20capital%20punishment.%20The%20silence%20and%20the%20blank%20expression%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20survivor%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mere%20child%20barely%2018%20years%20of%20age%2C%20spoke%20volumes.%20We%20tried%20to%20draw%20her%20out%20and%20finally%20got%20the%20hint%20of%20an%20impish%20smile%20when%20we%20urged%20her%20to%20think%20about%20herself%20and%20to%20tell%20us%20what%20she%20wants%20rather%20than%20what%20others%20want%20for%20her!%20She%20was%20able%20to%20articulate%20what%20she%20wanted%20and%20that%20was%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20and%20power%20of%20women%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20divide%20is%20simply%20astounding%20and%20also%20very%20complicated.%20As%20one%20of%20our%20team%20members%20put%20it%2C%20she%20has%20never%20seen%20this%20kind%20of%20spirit%20and%20resistance%20across%20the%20country.%20We%20met%20Kuki%20women%20sitting%20in%20the%20pelting%20rain%20and%20thick%20fog%20at%20Tengnoupal%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20blocking%20the%20movement%20of%20RAF%20Commando%20trucks%20on%20the%20Trans%20Asian%20highway%20to%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh.%20We%20saw%20too%20the%20sensitivity%20and%20gentleness%20of%20a%20group%20of%20young%20women%20who%20have%20encircled%20a%20young%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20her%20family%20moving%20them%20out%20from%20a%20very%20public%20relief%20camp%20and%20helping%20to%20set%20up%20a%20home%20in%20a%20beautiful%20and%20secure%20homestead%20enabling%20healing%20and%20freeing%20them%20from%20constant%20media%20and%20public%20focus%20and%20supporting%20the%20whole%20family%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM.jpg%201198w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM-1022x1024.jpg%201022w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16113158%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.31.33-AM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668282%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20encountered%20the%20absolutely%20formidable%20force%20and%20power%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20as%20they%20enforced%20a%20Public%20curfew%20in%20Meitei%20districts%2C%20blocked%20access%20to%20Kuki%20dominated%20areas%20or%20organised%2Fparticipated%20in%20collective%20mourning%20for%20a%20slain%20youth%20from%20the%20security%20forces.%20We%20saw%20their%20power%20but%20have%20come%20back%20with%20troubling%20as%20well%20as%20complex%20questions%20about%20their%20%E2%80%98agency%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20strong%20patriarchal%20society%20like%20theirs.%20What%20was%20quite%20evident%20though%20was%20that%20unlike%20women%20from%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20communities%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20general%20do%20not%20appear%20to%20come%20under%20any%20Unified%20Command%20Structure%20and%20therefore%20defy%20any%20attempts%20at%20disciplining.%20In%20our%20team%20itself%20there%20were%20disagreements%20about%20this%20structure%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20but%20it%20was%20obvious%20that%20while%20a%20loose%20and%20amorphous%20structure%20allows%20for%20autonomy%20and%20resilience%20at%20the%20local%20level%20as%20each%20Leikai%20or%20locality%20has%20its%20own%20group%20of%20Meira%20Paibis%20with%20different%20operating%20styles%20and%20norms%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20hugely%20chaotic%20and%20unrestrainable.%20A%20keen%20sense%20of%20justice%20and%20defiance%20against%20subjugation%20or%20oppression%20is%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20the%20political%20consciousness%20of%20Meitei%20women%20in%20general%20and%20in%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20particular.%20For%20lack%20of%20autonomy%20within%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20their%20home%2C%20the%20expression%20of%20this%20political%20consciousness%20in%20the%20public%20space%20is%20immensely%20important%20to%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20and%20to%20their%20sense%20of%20being%2C%20and%20this%20is%20their%20driving%20force.%20While%20this%20is%20their%20strength%2C%20it%20is%20also%20their%20vulnerability%2C%20as%20vested%20interests%20from%20even%20among%20them%2C%20can%20so%20easily%20manipulate%20it%20in%20any%20which%20way.%20There%20is%20enough%20evidence%20coming%20in%20to%20show%20that%20%E2%80%98lines%20were%20crossed%E2%80%99%20and%20extremely%20negative%20roles%20were%20played%20by%20sections%20of%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20the%20present%20conflict%20and%20that%20at%20certain%20moments%20of%20the%20conflict%20there%20was%20manipulation.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20justification%20for%20these%20roles%2C%20but%20neither%20can%20there%20be%20sweeping%20generalizations%20and%20condemnation%20for%20all.%20The%20question%20then%20is%20how%20to%20%E2%80%98channelise%E2%80%99%20this%20political%20consciousness%20and%20this%20resistance%20to%20stay%20focussed%20on%20a%20community%20enhancing%20rather%20than%20community%20dividing%20approach%2C%20that%20can%20form%20the%20core%20of%20peace%20building%20efforts.%20It%20is%20a%20daunting%20task%20but%20not%20impossible%2C%20and%20very%20tiny%20baby%20steps%20have%20already%20been%20initiated%20quietly%20at%20the%20local%20level%20by%20women%20who%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20or%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Kuki%20side%20we%20also%20met%20and%20interacted%20at%20length%20with%20young%20women%2C%20educated%20in%20Universities%20outside%20Manipur%20but%20who%20are%20now%20back%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20who%20provided%20a%20refreshingly%20different%20and%20gendered%20perspective%20and%20analysis%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20ethnic%20divide%20and%20the%20stereotypical%20role%20of%20men%20in%20general%20including%20men%20from%20their%20own%20community.%20They%20were%20enraged%20that%20men%20who%20cannot%20manage%20their%20personal%20lives%20are%20entrusted%20with%20managing%20the%20country%2C%20with%20the%20mess%20that%20men%20as%20%E2%80%98decision%20makers%E2%80%99%20from%20Delhi%20down%20to%20the%20local%20level%20have%20created%20and%20of%20women%20being%20caught%20in%20between%2C%20and%20having%20to%20attend%20to%20and%20clean%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98mess%E2%80%99!%20These%20women%20were%20grateful%20and%20appreciative%20of%20the%20opportunity%20to%20interact%20with%20our%20team%2C%20air%20their%20frustrations%20and%20share%20their%20thoughts%2C%20as%20they%20were%20fed%20up%20of%20answering%20mechanical%20questions%20posed%20to%20them%20by%20visiting%20media%20teams%20and%20others.%20They%20were%20also%20able%20to%20discuss%20at%20length%20and%20in%20a%20balanced%20and%20unbiased%20manner%20the%20role%20that%20social%20media%20and%20fake%20news%20has%20played%20in%20fuelling%20the%20conflict.%20Many%20of%20the%20older%20women%20also%20felt%20that%20the%20strategy%20of%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%2C%20of%20having%20appointed%20advisors%20from%20outside%20with%20right%20wing%20links%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20listening%20to%20voices%20from%20the%20ground%20is%20also%20a%20critical%20contributory%20factor%20to%20the%20present%20catastrophe%20and%20to%20determining%20the%20hate%20filled%20political%20narrative%20of%20the%20state%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20SHOULD%20WE%20BE%20THINKING%20ABOUT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Manipur%20has%20witnessed%20several%20episodes%20of%20violent%20conflicts%20over%20the%20years.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20civilisational%20control%20and%20norms%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20lost%2C%20and%20lines%20of%20control%20crossed%20like%20never%20before.%20If%20this%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20by%20both%20sides%2C%20then%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Convention%20as%20well%20as%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Meitei%20War%20principles%20and%20the%20Tribal%20war%20principles%20which%20predate%20Geneva%20have%20been%20grossly%20violated.%20The%20fact%20that%20lines%20have%20been%20crossed%20is%20indeed%20alarming%20as%20is%20indicated%20by%20the%20numerous%20cases%20of%20brutal%20sexual%20violence%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20ambulances%20carrying%20the%20injured%20were%20waylaid%20and%20attacked%20even%20as%20convention%20dictates%20that%20hospitals%20and%20health%20services%20be%20exempt%20from%20attacks%20in%20even%20the%20most%20brutal%20of%20wars.%20These%20tragic%20instances%20raise%20the%20question%20as%20to%20why%20such%20lines%20were%20crossed%3F%20In%20any%20process%20of%20peace%20building%20this%20question%20will%20have%20to%20be%20thoroughly%20probed%20and%20factored%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Killings%20and%20death%20is%20inevitable%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20or%20in%20the%20process%20of%20%E2%80%98defense%E2%80%99%20but%20what%20is%20not%20acceptable%20and%20was%20strongly%20condemned%20across%20sections%20is%20the%20levels%20of%20barbarity.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20initiate%20some%20conversations%20on%20the%20levels%20of%20barbarity%20with%20the%20Meiteis%20but%20it%20was%20only%20with%20the%20more%20progressive%20people.%20More%20in-depth%20engagement%20is%20required%20and%20with%20a%20wider%20cross%20section%20of%20people%20of%20both%20the%20communities%20including%20with%20the%20Meira%20Paibis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20systematic%20clampdown%20on%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20dissenting%20local%20voices%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20and%20the%20promotion%20and%20patronisation%20of%20vigilante%20groups%20that%20toe%20the%20political%20line%20has%20obliterated%20or%20systematically%20suppressed%20an%20important%20section%20of%20credible%20voices%20that%20help%20to%20maintain%20a%20level%20of%20checks%20and%20balances%20that%20keeps%20together%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20communities.%20In%20conflict%20affected%20Manipur%20this%20has%20always%20been%20of%20particular%20significance.%20The%20BJP%20regime%E2%80%99s%20coercive%20approach%20has%20enabled%20the%20hijacking%20of%20rational%20and%20societal%20building%20voices%20by%20the%20divisive%20and%20hate%20filled%20agenda%20of%20the%20state%20supported%20non%20state%20groups.%20The%20blanket%20impunity%20provided%20to%20such%20forces%20and%20select%20CSOs%20by%20the%20State%20has%20totally%20emboldened%20such%20groups%2C%20given%20them%20a%20sense%20of%20complete%20security%20and%20enabled%20them%20and%20not%20the%20progressive%20voices%20to%20control%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20There%20is%20a%20huge%20proliferation%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20ranging%20from%20light%20machine%20and%20combat%20guns%20to%20mortars%20and%20rocket%20launchers.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20the%20arms%20were%20both%20looted%20or%20handed%20over%20upon%20production%20of%20%E2%80%98aadhar%20cards%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20police%20stations%20and%20depots!%20We%20saw%20people%20moving%20around%20with%20AK%2047s%20casually%20slung%20over%20their%20shoulders%20clad%20in%20casuals%20or%20in%20military%20fatigues!%20As%20army%20fatigues%20were%20also%20looted%20and%20widely%20distributed%2C%20oftentimes%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20distinguish%20between%20a%20civilian%20in%20%E2%80%98defense%E2%80%99%20role%20versus%20state%20security%20forces!%20The%20availability%20of%20this%20level%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20in%20a%20state%20with%20an%20extensive%20international%20border%20is%20deeply%20disturbing%20and%20totally%20incomprehensible%20from%20a%20National%20Security%20point%20of%20view.%20It%20totally%20defies%20one%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20and%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98internal%20security%E2%80%99%20and%20of%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Government%20in%20question%20to%20be%20in%20control.%20In%20Manipur%20today%20who%20is%20in%20control%20has%20become%20a%20guessing%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%98toxic%20masculinity%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20need%20to%20form%20a%20network%20of%20exposed%20young%20men%20from%20both%20communities%20to%20work%20against%20it%20was%20also%20raised%20by%20a%20PhD%20researcher%20%E2%80%93%20a%20young%20man%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20We%20encountered%20shelling%2C%20gunshots%20and%20aggressive%20tear%20gassing%20at%20different%20places%20and%20at%20different%20moments%20of%20our%20visit.%20One%20night%20we%20were%20housed%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20his%20family%20and%20prevented%20from%20going%20back%20to%20our%20hotel%20by%20the%20relentless%20onslaught%20of%20peppered%20tear%20gas%20and%20gunshots%20and%20witnessed%20the%20reaction%20and%20trauma%20of%20his%20little%20children.%20We%20wondered%20about%20the%20collective%20trauma%20of%20children%20across%20the%20ethnic%20divides%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20last%20three%20months!%20And%20yet%20instead%20of%20working%20towards%20finding%20a%20sincere%20solution%2C%20it%20is%20whataboutery%20that%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20indulge%20in.%20What%20if%20their%20own%20children%20were%20caught%20up%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20was%20our%20question%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20issue%20of%20illegal%20migration%20of%20people%20from%20across%20the%201700-km-long%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20was%20repeatedly%20mentioned%20as%20a%20key%20trigger%20of%20the%20present%20conflict%20by%20the%20Meiteis.%20There%20were%20allegations%20by%20both%20sides%20that%20border%20management%20which%20lies%20with%20the%20Centre%20is%20pathetically%20run%20or%20deliberately%20mismanaged.%20Picking%20up%20on%20the%20question%20of%20poor%20management%20of%20the%20border%20issues%2C%20the%20Kuki%20leaders%20pointed%20out%20that%20with%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20the%20extensive%20human%20rights%20violations%20by%20the%20military%20junta%2C%20crossing%20over%20of%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20is%20inevitable.%20India%20needs%20to%20urgently%20formulate%20a%20clear%20Refugee%20Policy%20guided%20by%20International%20standards%20and%20play%20a%20role%20on%20Refugee%20protection%20as%20an%20Asian%20leader.%20They%20further%20reiterated%20that%20there%20should%20be%20clear%20guidelines%20to%20identify%20refugees%20so%20that%20genuine%20Indian%20citizens%20are%20not%20repeatedly%20harassed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20immediate%20as%20well%20as%20long%20term%20fallout%20of%20the%20present%20conflict%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20internally%20displaced%20people%2C%20which%20needs%20urgent%20attention.%20In%20the%20relief%20camps%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20relief%20camps%20itself%20and%20the%20horror%20that%20drove%20people%20to%20these%20camps%2C%20the%20large%20looming%20question%20on%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20face%20was%20about%20their%20uncertain%20future%20and%20status.%20The%20issue%20of%20IDPs%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20raised%20by%20human%20rights%20and%20relief%20workers%20in%20the%20past%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20certainly%20calls%20for%20urgently%20pushing%20for%20an%20IDP%20policy%20to%20be%20drafted%20and%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20There%20is%20undoubtedly%20an%20angle%20of%20dwindling%20land%20resources%20and%20increased%20populations%20making%20claims%20on%20the%20limited%20land%20and%20the%20tension%20around%20this.%20An%20opinion%20that%20was%20expressed%20from%20the%20Meitei%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Nagas%20was%20that%20perhaps%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20stop%20the%20%E2%80%98recognition%E2%80%99%20of%20new%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20The%20clear%20cut%20agenda%20of%20bringing%20about%20a%20communal%20divide%20along%20religious%20lines%20by%20the%20right%20wing%20Hindutva%20forces%20was%20strongly%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Kuki%20side%20with%20documented%20evidence.%20On%20the%20Meitei%20side%2C%20while%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20and%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20(which%20appears%20to%20be%20more%20like%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20private%20army)%20is%20loud%20and%20clear%2C%20opinions%20are%20divided%20about%20the%20actual%20control%20and%20power%20of%20the%20communal%20forces%20over%20the%20Meitei%20ethos.%20Some%20are%20reluctant%20to%20give%20them%20more%20importance%20and%20power%20than%20they%20actually%20have%2C%20some%20wonder%20whether%20they%20can%20be%20used%20while%20yet%20others%20see%20them%20being%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20hate%20filled%20agenda.%20Whatever%20be%20the%20various%20opinions%2C%20the%20insidious%20inroads%20of%20Indian%20right%20wing%20forces%20into%20Meitei%20society%2C%20having%20a%20clearcut%20agenda%20especially%20in%20districts%20like%20Bishenpur%2C%20where%20there%20are%20large%20numbers%20of%20followers%20of%20the%20indigenous%20Sanamahi%20faith%20cannot%20be%20trivialized.%20They%20are%20there%20with%20their%20agenda%20advancing%20stealthily%2C%20fraying%20and%20diluting%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20Meitei%20ethos%20and%20sense%20of%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Narco%20Terrorism%20is%20a%20phrase%20that%20is%20bandied%20around%20by%20all%20and%20sundry%20but%20it%20is%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20great%20concern.%20That%20there%20is%20a%20nexus%20between%20the%20politically%20powerful%2C%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20elections%20and%20drug%20cartels%20is%20obvious%20enough%20but%20it%20is%20an%20extremely%20murky%20and%20violent%20world%20and%20beyond%20the%20reach%20of%20common%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESURVIVING%20%3A%20ON%20RELIEF%20AND%20REHABILITATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20relief%20camps%20in%20Moirang%2C%20Tengnoupal%20and%20Kangpokpi.%20Camps%20in%20Moirang%20had%20mostly%20Meitei%20people%20and%20the%20camps%20in%20other%20two%20places%20had%20displaced%20people%20belonging%20to%20Kuki-Zo%20communities.%20These%20camps%20were%20housed%20in%20school%20and%20college%20premises.%20This%20has%20meant%20that%20educational%20activities%20in%20these%20spaces%20have%20come%20to%20a%20halt%20since%20the%20last%203%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20presence%20appeared%20to%20be%20absent%20or%20minimal%20in%20the%20relief%20Camps.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20when%20the%20conflict%20began%20much%20of%20the%20relief%20arrangements%20were%20being%20done%20by%20community%20groups%20particularly%20the%20localities%20where%20these%20camps%20came%20up.%20In%20fact%20it%20is%20only%20now%2C%203%20months%20later%20that%20the%20state%20is%20attempting%20to%20intervene%20by%20way%20of%20relief.%20However%2C%20the%20relief%20is%20still%20far%20from%20satisfactory.%20The%20living%20conditions%20in%20the%20camps%20continue%20to%20be%20difficult.%20Only%20two%20substantial%20meals%20consisting%20mostly%20of%20rice%20and%20dal%20are%20served%20twice%20a%20day%20and%20not%20much%20is%20provided%20in%20between%2C%20not%20even%20morning%20tea%2C%20which%20the%20people%20have%20expressed%20is%20very%20difficult%20especially%20for%20the%20elderly%20and%20the%20children.%20Children%20have%20no%20access%20to%20other%20snacks.%20Mattresses%20have%20been%20spread%20out%20on%20the%20floors%20of%20the%20rooms%20and%20with%20the%20rains%20the%20rooms%20double%20up%20as%20a%20space%20for%20drying%20clothes.%20This%20makes%20the%20atmosphere%20damp%20and%20poses%20a%20health%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20privacy.%20Men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20are%20sharing%20the%20same%20space.%20Pregnant%20and%20lactating%20mothers%20are%20also%20not%20provided%20separate%20space.%20Mothers%20and%20pregnant%20women%20lacked%20necessities%20such%20as%20thermos%20and%20hot%20water%20bags%20which%20were%20then%20provided%20by%20the%20community%20groups%20in%20some%20places.%20PDS%20provisions%20have%20not%20reached%20the%20camps.%20In%20fact%20PDS%20has%20not%20reached%20the%20districts%20in%20the%20past%203%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20dedicated%20health%20services%20in%20the%20camps%2C%20just%20informal%20arrangements%20with%20locality%20medicine%20shops%20for%20providing%20medicines%20where%20necessary.%20No%20psychosocial%20counseling%20is%20being%20provided%20and%20as%20one%20of%20the%20camp%20persons%20expressed%20that%20she%20feels%20there%20is%20no%20one%20she%20can%20share%20her%20sorrow%20with%20even%20though%20there%20are%20many%20people%20in%20the%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%20has%20come%20to%20a%20complete%20halt%20and%20is%20a%20big%20concern%20especially%20for%20parents%20of%20those%20who%20are%20in%20class%2010%20and%2012.%20There%20are%20concerns%20about%20their%20board%20exams%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20camp%20members%20have%20also%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20work%20and%20some%20camp%20residents%20are%20compelled%20to%20leave%20the%20camps%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20Some%20community%20groups%20have%20initiated%20livelihood%20activities%20in%20some%20camps%20but%20have%20expressed%20that%20this%20is%20merely%20a%20stop%20gap%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20persons%20who%20arrived%20at%20the%20camps%20have%20subsequently%20also%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20camps%20and%20are%20residing%20with%20relatives%20in%20the%20state%20or%20outside%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20question%20that%20is%20left%20unanswered%20is%20rehabilitation.%20How%20and%20when%20can%20those%20in%20the%20camps%20safely%20return%3F%20How%20will%20they%20rebuild%20their%20homes%20that%20have%20been%20destroyed%3F%20Many%20including%20community%20relief%20camp%20committee%20members%20are%20raising%20this%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20observations%20and%20information%20gathered%20after%20interactions%20with%20those%20in%20the%20camps%20and%20the%20volunteers%20and%20community%20groups%20the%20following%20suggestions%20are%20being%20made%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM-300x272.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115011%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.46.02-AM-1024x928.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668284%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221087%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAN%20THERE%20BE%20ANY%20FINAL%20THOUGHTS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20go%20back%20from%20the%20Manipur%20battleground%20with%20a%20high%20level%20of%20despondency.%20Our%20team%20experienced%20the%20same%20sadness%2C%20depression%20and%20sense%20of%20futility.%20The%20strange%20refusal%20of%20the%20PM%20to%20say%20anything%20till%20pushed%2C%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20the%20apathy%20of%20the%20Centre%20to%20the%20state%20and%20to%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict.%20At%20another%20level%20though%2C%20it%20also%20appears%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20militaristic%20strategy%20of%20tiring%20out%20your%20opponents%20by%20making%20them%20%E2%80%98wait%E2%80%99%20it%20out.%20We%20could%20see%20the%20fatigue%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20women%20on%20both%20sides%20who%20were%20out%20protesting%20or%20grappling%20against%20emerging%20crises%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20The%20class%20and%20economic%20dimensions%20of%20peoples%20suffering%20and%20how%20they%20will%20rebuild%20their%20lives%20is%20also%20quite%20apparent.%20Without%20a%20doubt%2C%20it%20is%20the%20poor%20and%20primarily%20the%20rural%20poor%20who%20will%20face%20the%20greatest%20challenge%20in%20rebuilding%20their%20lives%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20That%20peoples%20and%20communities%20are%20expendable%20was%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20seemed%20to%20run%20through%20all%20the%20State%20action%20or%20inaction.%20Yet%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20could%20not%20but%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98spirit%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20continued%20%E2%80%98resistance%E2%80%99%20against%20all%20odds.%20We%20heard%20numerous%20accounts%20of%20people%20cutting%20across%20communities%20helping%20each%20other%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20violence.%20These%20voices%20have%20mostly%20been%20drowned%20in%20the%20overwhelming%20narrative%20of%20violence%2C%20but%20needs%20to%20be%20picked%20up%20and%20heard.%20Finally%2C%20it%20is%20Regina%E2%80%99s%20words%20that%20we%20carry%20back%20with%20us.%20She%20said%20%E2%80%9C%20We%20have%20hope%20and%20we%20cling%20to%20it%20for%20it%20cannot%20be%20taken%20away%20from%20us.%20Hope%20is%20all%20that%20we%20have%20left%20after%20our%20houses%20and%20homes%20have%20been%20burnt%2C%20our%20fields%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%2C%20our%20places%20of%20worship%20gone%20and%20our%20social%20lives%20ripped%20apart%E2%80%9D.%20We%20parted%20in%20hope%20that%20we%20would%20find%20more%20such%20voices%20in%20the%20period%20ahead%20and%20that%20we%20may%20join%20hands%20towards%20healing%20and%20rebuilding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115131%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.51.05-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115131%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.51.05-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115131%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.51.05-AM-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115131%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.51.05-AM-1024x682.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPOSTSCRIPT%20%2F%20SNAPSHOTS%20FROM%20MANIPUR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSyeda%20Hameed%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20sense%20I%20am%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%20The%20word%20LoC%20is%20bandied%20around.%20Barricades%20are%20visible%20everywhere.%20It%20is%20a%20war%20zone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20two%20countries%20are%20struggling%20to%20be%20born.%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%2C%20in%20full%20battle%20gear%2C%20are%20ranged%20on%20either%20side.%20AK%2047%2C%20bombs%2C%20hand%20grenades.%20Sights%20and%20sounds%20which%20send%20a%20chill%20body%20signal.%20I%20am%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20small%20delegation%20of%204%20women.%203%20from%20the%20North%20East%20and%20me.%20I%2C%20Kashmir%20born%2C%20partition%20torn%2C%20stand%20on%20the%20debris%20of%20a%20land%20that%20is%20rightly%20known%20as%20the%20most%20precious%20jewel%20of%20India.%20I%20stand%20here%20because%20since%20the%20last%2020%20years%20when%20Kangla%20Fort%20was%20handed%20to%20people%2C%20I%20have%20identified%20with%20Manipur.%20Today%20we%20are%20in%20mourning.%20Wamiq%20Jaunpuri%20wrote%20these%20lines%20%E2%80%98Who%20will%20answer%3F%E2%80%99%20when%20Gandhiji%20was%20assassinated.%20Today%20they%20resonate%20with%20Manipur%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYe%20kaun%20qatl%20ho%20gaya%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EYe%20kaun%20dil%20ka%20raaz%20sabse%20kehte%20kehte%20so%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EJawab%20iska%20kaun%20de%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EKe%20khud%20hamare%20haath%20iss%20lahu%20mein%20hain%20rangey%20huey%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20has%20been%20killed%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnWho%20has%20been%20put%20to%20sleep%20while%20pouring%20out%20his%20heart%3F%20Who%20will%20answer%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%3F%20But%20our%20hands%20are%20dyed%20in%20the%20same%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20my%20thoughts%20which%20I%20need%20to%20express%20while%20they%20rage%20within%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScene%20One%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20rise%20on%20the%20mind.%20We%20are%20on%20our%20way%20to%20Churachandpur.%20We%20reach%20Kwatka%20Bazar%2C%20a%20Pangal-Muslim%20village.%20It%20is%20raining.%20Hundreds%20of%20women%20are%20sitting%20in%20partly%20covered%20shelters%20along%20the%20road%20which%20leads%20to%20the%20LoC%20dividing%20Bishnupur%20from%20Churachandpur.%20Hundreds%20of%20men%20swarm%20around%2C%20many%20with%20guns.%203%20Meiteis%2C%20father-son%20and%20their%20friend%20have%20been%20butchered%20then%20shot%20at%203%20AM.%20Their%20bodies%20are%20still%20lying%20there.%E2%80%98%20Pay%20your%20respects%E2%80%99%20we%20are%20asked.%20I%20cover%20my%20head%20with%20my%20namaaz%20scarf.%20We%20walk%20towards%20the%20women.%20In%20their%20midst%20is%20the%20young%20wife%20of%20the%20victim.%20My%20colleagues%20bend%20down%20to%20hug%20her%20trembling%20form%20and%20let%20their%20tears%20mingle%20with%20hers.%20We%20hear%20shots%2C%20cross%20firing%20very%20close%3B%20my%20heart%20lurches.%20This%20is%20the%20end%20but%20we%20cannot%20move.%20I%20have%20just%20finished%20mourning%20for%20the%20martyrs%20of%20Karbala%3B%20Bishnupur%20and%20Churachandpur%20are%20also%20Karbala.%20We%20get%20up%20and%20move%20to%20the%20car%3B%20a%20man%20appears%20at%20the%20window.%20%E2%80%98He%20is%20Nobo%20Volcano%2C%20beloved%20Manipuri%20singer.%E2%80%99%20someone%20says.%20In%20a%20loud%20voice%20he%20shouts%20into%20the%20cameras%20being%20held%20before%20his%20face.%20%E2%80%98%20Modi!%20We%20voted%20you%20in%3B%20in%20the%20centre%20and%20state.%20And%20you%3F%20You%20have%20betrayed%20us.%20You%20have%20let%20us%20butcher%20each%20other%2C%20rape%20and%20kill%20our%20daughters%20while%20you%20and%20your%20Manipur%20colleague%20are%20watching%20from%20your%20far%20off%20high%20perches.%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%5CnFour%20of%20us%20plus%20two%20of%20the%20brightest%20and%20kindest%20women%20from%20this%20state%20who%20have%20accompanied%20us%2C%20sit%20in%20stunned%20silence%20while%20word%20comes%20from%20the%20border%20that%20any%20further%20movement%20is%20fraught%20with%20danger.%20We%20turn%20back.%20We%20were%20just%2015%20kms%20from%20the%20Line%20of%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScene%20Two%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20it%20were%20the%20Kuki%20we%20saw%20as%20we%20entered%20district%20Tengnopal%20from%20Imphal.%20The%20last%20post%2C%20Moreh%20is%2030%20kms%20from%20Burma%20border.%20Moreh%20is%20where%20long%20ago%20we%20went%20for%20shopping%20for%20gadgets%20smuggled%