%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fgermany-and-spain-in-contest-for-4-8-billion-indian-submarine-deal-123081600196_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fgermany-and-spain-in-contest-for-4-8-billion-indian-submarine-deal-123081600196_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fgermany-and-spain-in-contest-for-4-8-billion-indian-submarine-deal-123081600196_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Zindagi%20Tamasha%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Gem%20From%20Pakistan%20That%20Shows%20Us%20the%20Dogma%20and%20Hypocrisy%20in%20%E2%80%98Upright%E2%80%99%20Society%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104618%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuhammad%20Rahat%20Khawaja%20(Arif%20Hassan)%20is%20a%20man%20of%20faith.%20Working%20as%20a%20real-estate%20broker%20in%20Lahore%20%E2%80%93%20a%20father%20of%20three%20daughters%20(all%20of%20them%20married%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20are%20settled%20abroad)%20%E2%80%93%20he%E2%80%99s%20popular%20for%20singing%20devotional%20hymns%20in%20praise%20of%20the%20Prophet.%20For%20all%20intents%20and%20purposes%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20an%20upstanding%20and%20respected%20member%20of%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emohalla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20is%20the%20case%20in%20most%20middle-class%20South%20Asian%20localities%2C%20neighbours%20often%20become%20as%20important%20as%20blood%20relations%2C%20if%20not%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rotund%2C%20mild-mannered%20Khawaja%20lives%20with%20his%20bed-ridden%20wife%20Farkhanda%20(Samiya%20Mumtaz)%2C%20while%20their%20daughter%20Sadaf%20(Eman%20Suleman)%20drops%20by%20every%20other%20day%2C%20after%20work.%20It%20becomes%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20the%20Khawaja%20household%20has%20stopped%20gendering%20their%20chores%2C%20something%20that%20probably%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20their%20neighbours.%20As%20we%20soon%20find%20out%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20that%20separates%20the%20Khawajas%20from%20the%20people%20around%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6PG92uSYLTQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhawaja%20takes%20an%20unusual%20amount%20of%20interest%20in%20films%2C%20especially%20in%20old%20heroines%20and%20their%20dance%20routines%20(not%20in%20the%20way%20you%E2%80%99re%20probably%20thinking).%20We%20see%20his%20eyes%20transfixed%20on%20a%20TV%20as%20he%20watches%20Aasia%20Begum%20perform%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZindagi%20Tamasha%20Bani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20song%20from%20a%20black-and-white%20Pakistani%20film%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENaukar%20Wohti%20Da%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1974)%20which%20also%20lends%20its%20name%20to%20the%20film.%20At%20a%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20wedding%2C%20the%20conversation%20turns%20towards%20how%20Khawaja%20liked%20to%20dress%20up%20and%20dance%20like%20heroines%20as%20a%20young%20boy.%20Playing%20along%20with%20the%20celebratory%20mood%20of%20the%20occasion%20and%20indulging%20his%20friends%2C%20Khawaja%20agrees%20to%20give%20them%20a%20glimpse%20of%20his%20devotion%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Aasia%20Begum.%20He%20recreates%20the%20heroine%E2%80%99s%20lascivious%20dance%20steps%2C%20and%20the%20giggles%20are%20soon%20replaced%20by%20awkward%20silence.%20The%20mood%20changes%20from%20faint%20bemusement%20to%20a%20tense%20stillness.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20someone%20films%20the%20performance%20and%20puts%20it%20on%20YouTube.%20It%20goes%20viral%2C%20and%20Khawaja%20becomes%20a%20subject%20of%20ridicule.%20Both%20at%20home%2C%20and%20outside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarmad%20Sultan%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20wishes%20to%20examine%20how%20civil%20society%20reacts%20when%20the%20tiniest%20bits%20of%20civilisation%20don%E2%80%99t%20fit%20into%20their%20predetermined%20mould.%20Khawaja%20sings%20for%20the%20Prophet%2C%20then%20how%20can%20he%20enjoy%20such%20a%20lecherous%20song%3F%20Or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20how%20dare%20he%20tap%20into%20his%20femininity%20to%20dance%20like%20his%20favourite%20heroine.%20Sadaf%2C%20a%20producer%20on%20a%20local%20news%20channel%2C%20chances%20upon%20the%20video%20on%20YouTube%20%E2%80%93%20and%20is%20almost%20immediately%20embarrassed%20of%20her%20father.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20when%20they%20first%20go%20home%20after%20discovering%20the%20video%2C%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20confront%20him.%20Her%20husband%20Danish%20(Ali%20Kureshi)%20speaks%20to%20her%20father%2C%20showing%20him%20the%20video%20and%20asking%20him%20about%20it.%20Although%20Sadaf%20could%20be%20part%20of%20the%20intellectual%20elite%2C%20her%20worldview%20proves%20to%20be%20more%20conservative%20than%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%2C%20who%20defends%20his%20father-in-law%20by%20denouncing%20the%20narrow-mindedness%20of%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104645%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.45.06-AM-1024x477.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668275%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22559%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Zindagi%20Tamasha%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20interrogates%20a%20society%20riddled%20with%20dogma%20and%20rigidity%2C%20which%20likes%20to%20stifle%20the%20slightest%20hints%20of%20happiness%20and%20pleasure%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20prescribed%20by%20it.%20The%20family-like%20neighbours%20start%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20Khawajas.%20The%20wedding%20invitations%20stop%2C%20some%20neighbours%20stop%20greeting%20him%20on%20the%20street%2C%20some%20send%20their%20kids%20to%20the%20doorstep%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20their%20home.%20On%20the%20day%20of%20Eid%2C%20some%20neighbours%20slam%20the%20door%20on%20his%20face%20when%20he%20offers%20them%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehalwa-puri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20we%E2%80%99re%20told%20the%20neighbours%20usually%20looked%20forward%20to.%20For%20all%20intents%20and%20purposes%2C%20the%20upstanding%20Khawaja%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20excommunicated%20by%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emohalla%20wallah%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20premiered%20at%20the%202019%20Busan%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20and%20has%20been%20battling%20for%20release%20for%20over%20four%20years.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20happened%20primarily%20because%20of%20one%20scene%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Khawaja%20is%20trying%20to%20record%20a%20video%20for%20a%20public%20apology%20to%20his%20friends%20and%20loved%20ones.%20A%20cleric%20oversees%20this%2C%20constantly%20interrupting%20Khawaja%20by%20saying%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20look%20%E2%80%98remorseful%20enough%E2%80%99.%20Khawaja%20lets%20it%20slide%20a%20few%20times%2C%20but%20slowly%20becomes%20agitated%20by%20the%20cleric%E2%80%99s%20condescension%2C%20and%20slams%20him%20for%20the%20boys%20getting%20sexually%20abused%20by%20clerics%20and%20Imams.%20This%20scene%20became%20the%20point%20of%20contention%20for%20political%20party%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Tehreek-E-Labbaik%2C%20which%20held%20widespread%20protests%2C%20calling%20the%20film%20%E2%80%98blasphemous%E2%80%99.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20in%20eerie%20poetic%20fashion%2C%20much%20like%20his%20protagonist%2C%20even%20Khoosat%20has%20been%20denounced%20by%20religious%20scholars%20and%20given%20death%20threats%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcontroversy-behind-joyland-explained%5C%22%3EWhy%20did%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Oscar%20Pick%20%E2%80%98Joyland%E2%80%99%20Stoke%20Controversy%20in%20the%20Country%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20compelling%20choices%20of%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20that%20its%20protagonist%20is%20no%20saint%20either.%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20acquaintance%20%E2%80%93%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20DVD-rental%20shop%2C%20Usman%20(Adeel%20Afzal)%20%E2%80%93%20invites%20him%20to%20a%20gathering.%20When%20he%20reaches%20there%2C%20Khawaja%20finds%20men%20drinking%2C%20while%20an%20effeminate-looking%20man%20(Sarmad%20Khoosat%20himself)%20dances%20for%20them.%20Usman%20tells%20him%20%E2%80%98be%20easy%E2%80%99%2C%20also%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cour%20kind%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahaul%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Usman%20assures%20Khawaja%20that%20no%20one%20would%20judge%20him%20for%20being%20himself.%20Offended%20at%20being%20identified%20as%20gay%2C%20Khawaja%20flings%20many%20homophobic%20slurs%20at%20Usman.%20According%20to%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%2C%20this%20is%20the%20real%20tragedy%20of%20a%20society%20fuelled%20by%20orthodoxy.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Khawaja%20judging%20Usman%2C%20or%20Sadaf%20judging%20her%20own%20father%20%E2%80%93%20everyone%20wants%20to%20be%20more%20pious%20than%20the%20next%20person%2C%20without%20anyone%20trying%20to%20understand%20each%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104633%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.44.50-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104633%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.44.50-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104633%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.44.50-AM-300x196.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104633%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.44.50-AM-1024x668.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668274%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22783%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Zindagi%20Tamasha%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20technically%20sharp%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20how%20it%20employs%20Saakin%20and%20Shamsher%20Rana%E2%80%99s%20music.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20sequence%20where%20Khawaja%20has%20been%20denied%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sing%20at%20an%20annual%20festivity.%20Saakin%20and%20Shamsher%20Rana%20compose%20a%20contemporary%20version%20of%20the%20hymn%20Khawaja%20had%20rehearsed%20%5B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAjj%20Sikk%20Mitraan%20Di%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%5D%2C%20as%20he%20walks%20back%20like%20a%20ghost.%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20vacant%20eyes%20at%20a%20sweet%20shop%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20haunting%20visuals%20in%20the%20film.%20Actor%20Arif%20Hassan%20shoulders%20the%20film%20with%20a%20performance%20that%20is%20superbly%20layered.%20His%20warmth%20next%20to%20his%20bed-ridden%20wife%2C%20the%20face%20of%20silent%20betrayal%20as%20everyone%20around%20abandons%20him%2C%20the%20defiance%20each%20time%20he%20faces%20his%20daughter%20as%20if%20asking%20her%20what%20is%20wrong%20about%20being%20himself.%20Khoosat%20also%20showcases%20Khawaja%20as%20a%20petty%20version%20of%20himself%2C%20when%20he%20goes%20and%20tells%20on%20Usman%E2%80%99s%20secret%20gatherings%20to%20the%20local%20police%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20way%20to%20measure%20up%20to%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98man%20of%20faith%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20own%20eyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20standout%20performance%20of%20the%20film%20is%20Khawaja%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Farkhanda.%20Samiya%20Mumtaz%E2%80%99s%20face%20is%20a%20beacon%20of%20empathy%2C%20grace%20and%20resolve.%20Some%20of%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20finest%20directorial%20touches%20are%20when%20a%20scene%20plays%20and%20he%20cuts%20to%20Farkhanda%20silently%20and%20powerlessly%20absorbing%20the%20events%20around%20her.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20her%20husband%20dancing%20along%20with%20heroines%20on%20TV%20in%20their%20living%20room%3B%20or%20when%20she%20wordlessly%20tries%20to%20be%20there%20for%20her%20daughter%20after%20she%E2%80%99s%20found%20the%20viral%20video.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20scenes%20in%20the%20film%2C%20she%20lies%20to%20him%20telling%20him%20she%20heard%20him%20sing%2C%20despite%20having%20gauged%20from%20his%20face%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20sing%20at%20the%20annual%20festivity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EZindagi%20Tamasha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20chilling%20portrait%20of%20a%20society%20that%20pays%20so%20much%20attention%20to%20the%20wheels%20of%20ideology%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20make%20note%20of%20the%20people%20being%20crushed%20or%20stifled%20under%20it%20everyday.%20Given%20the%20current%20state%20of%20creative%20conservatism%20permeating%20the%20arts%20in%20India%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20circus%20that%20is%20about%20to%20ensue%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20course-correct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20film%20is%20available%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxUkJEnHCaos%26ab_channel%3DKhoosatFilms%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692163855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16104618%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fzindagi-tamasha-pakistan-sarmad-sultan-khoosat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Director%20Sarmad%20Sultan%20Khoosat%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20stuck%20for%20a%20proper%20release%20since%202019%20because%20conservative%20elements%20have%20objected%20to%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fzindagi-tamasha-pakistan-sarmad-sultan-khoosat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20All%20Matters%20Debatable%2C%20the%20Opposition%20Owned%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16093212%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-9.30.17-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20pointed%20out%20a%20stark%20contradiction%20in%20her%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20speech.%20Opposing%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20she%20noted%20that%20while%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20attempts%20to%20wrest%20bureaucratic%20control%20from%20the%20elected%20Delhi%20government%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20successively%20promised%20full%20statehood%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20in%20its%20election%20manifestos%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESule%2C%20who%20has%20received%20the%20best%20parliamentarian%20award%20multiple%20times%20since%202014%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20who%20spoke%20about%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doublespeak%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20monsoon%20session%20of%20Parliament.%20A%20range%20of%20Opposition%20MPs%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20took%20turns%20to%20corner%20the%20Union%20government%20by%20identifying%20instances%20and%20issues%20where%20the%20Modi-led%20NDA%20government%20has%20acted%20decidedly%20against%20cooperative%20federalism%2C%20%3Cem%3Esabka%20saath%2C%20sabka%20vikaas%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20scam-free%20governance%2C%20which%20constantly%20feature%20in%20its%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inimitable%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%2C%20questioned%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20poor%20attendance%20in%20Parliament%2C%20lampooning%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Cif%20not%20Modi%2C%20who%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20Congress%20leader%20Manish%20Tewari%20brought%20out%20references%20to%20highlight%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%20on%20national%20security%20matters%2C%20especially%20the%20continuing%20Chinese%20aggression%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20borders.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20led%20from%20the%20front%20to%20attack%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20arrogance%20and%20indifference%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20sectarian%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20and%20communal%20violence%20in%20Haryana.%20Backing%20the%20INDIA%20MPs%20were%20leaders%20like%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20who%20invoked%20rising%20radicalisation%20among%20Hindus%20in%20India%20while%20speaking%20about%20the%20recent%20selective%20killing%20of%20some%20Muslim%20men%20by%20a%20railway%20cop%20in%20a%20moving%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20the%202023%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20Tells%20Us%20About%20the%20State%20of%20Governance%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmonsoon-session-parliament-laws-discussion%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%202023%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20Tells%20Us%20About%20the%20State%20of%20Governance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20matters%20debatable%2C%20the%20monsoon%20session%20belonged%20to%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20displayed%20rare%20unity%20in%20its%20ranks%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Union%20government%20rushed%20through%2023%20bills%20with%20its%20brute%20majority.%20The%20monsoon%20session%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20first%20test%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20ideological%20unity.%20Through%20the%20course%20of%20the%20session%2C%20INDIA%20MPs%20showed%20that%20the%20Opposition%20grouping%20is%20not%20a%20loose%20coalition%20brought%20together%20without%20a%20plan.%20Its%20leaders%20coordinated%2C%20acted%20and%20performed%20in%20unison.%20They%20met%20daily%20to%20decide%20on%20a%20common%20plan%20of%20action%2C%20unitedly%20appeared%20dressed%20in%20black%20to%20protest%20against%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20Manipur%2C%20and%20even%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Houses%20together.%20More%20importantly%2C%20they%20appeared%20to%20be%20serious%20about%20sticking%20together%20despite%20occasional%20differences%2C%20as%20could%20be%20seen%20when%20all%20of%20them%20eventually%20agreed%20to%20a%20no-trust%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20MPs%20had%20no%20new%20weapon%20in%20their%20armour.%20As%20always%2C%20they%20invoked%20their%20hackneyed%20nationalist%20credentials%2C%20aggressively%20defended%20their%20government%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20contentious%20government%20data%2C%20and%20indulged%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ead%20hominem%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eattacks%20on%20Opposition%20leaders%20without%20feeling%20the%20need%20to%20offer%20a%20fresh%20perspective%2C%20or%20a%20narrative%2C%20in%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3Eprime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20that%20lasted%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20resembled%20most%20of%20his%20previous%20speeches%2C%20including%20his%20focus%20on%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20much%20more%20than%20recounting%20his%20achievements.%20Modi%20and%20his%20ministers%E2%80%99%20attempt%20to%20discount%20INDIA%20as%20%E2%80%9CI.dot%2C%20N.dot%2C%20D.dot%2C%20I.dot%2C%20A.dot%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20speeches%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20dismissing%20the%20newly-formed%20Opposition%20grouping%20as%20%E2%80%9CGhamandiya%E2%80%9D%20reflected%20the%20communication%20crisis%20that%20has%20plagued%20the%20BJP%20ever%20since%20the%20strategically-named%20INDIA%20bloc%20emerged.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20preempted%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20line%20of%20attack%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Ehit%20out%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Carrogance%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20not%20intervening%20urgently%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20he%20effectively%20nullified%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20constant%20referring%20to%20INDIA%20as%20%E2%80%9CGhamandiya%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98No%20Trace%20of%20Sympathy%E2%80%99%3A%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20Reply%20to%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Parliament%20Was%20an%20Insult%20to%20Manipur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-trace-of-sympathy-modi-shahs-reply-to-the-opposition-in-parliament-was-an-insult-to-manipur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98No%20Trace%20of%20Sympathy%E2%80%99%3A%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20Reply%20to%20the%