llegal%20weapons%20and%20threatening%20behaviour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20complaint%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2015-20%20people%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20charged%20under%20various%20sections%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrangi%20had%20been%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20month%20for%20a%20provocative%20video%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20on%20July%2031%20morning%2C%20but%20was%20then%20released%20on%20bail.%20He%20has%20previously%20also%20featured%20in%20multiple%20hate%20speech-related%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692161604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16102201%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.21.32-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbajrang-dal-leader-bittu-bajrangi-arrested-in-nuh-violence-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20police%20officer's%20complaint%20accused%20Bajrangi%20of%20snatching%20weapons%20from%20the%20police%20during%20the%20'Shobha%20Yatra'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbajrang-dal-leader-bittu-bajrangi-arrested-in-nuh-violence-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Headmaster%20collapses%20after%20unfurling%20flag%20in%20Odisha%20school%2C%20dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692159126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102759139%2Cimgsize-16452.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhubaneswar%2Fheadmaster-collapses-after-unfurling-tricolour-at-school-in-odisha-dies%2Farticleshow%2F102759087.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20headmaster%20of%20a%20primary%20school%20in%20Krushnaprasad%20block%20in%20Puri%20district%20in%20Odisha%20collapsed%20after%20unfurling%20the%20tricolour%20at%20his%20school%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANDIP%20MISHRA%22