uced%20to%20debris%2C%20Mohammed%20is%20hurt%20but%20not%20hopeless.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20damaged%20many%20Muslim%20homes%20and%20lives%2C%20but%20we%20will%20stand%20again%2C%20In%20Sha%20Allah%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mohammed%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutsiders%E2%80%99%20yatra%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Devi%2C%2060%2C%20a%20local%20of%20Nuh%2C%20has%20been%20living%20in%20the%20area%20for%20decades%20now%20and%20has%20never%20seen%20anything%20even%20close%20to%20the%20fear%20she%20saw%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20her%20Muslim%20neighbours%2C%20escaping%20violence%20they%20were%20uninvolved%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20yatra%2C%20we%20could%20see%20how%20outsiders%20were%20instigating%20Muslims.%20These%20were%20not%20the%20Hindus%20we%20have%20here%20in%20Nuh.%20This%20is%20not%20Hinduism%2C%20Bajrang%20Dal%20has%20wronged%20even%20Hindus%20by%20using%20the%20religious%20procession%20to%20create%20chaos%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20field%20visit%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%20in%20Nuh%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20locals%20that%20the%20Yatra%20had%20taken%20place%20thrice%20before%20July%202023%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20had%20never%20before%20met%20the%20same%20fate.%20Just%20as%20the%20previous%20years%2C%20this%20year%20too%2C%20local%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20offered%20cold%20water%20to%20the%20yatris%2C%20as%20they%20also%20remember%20offering%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekanwariyas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20Singh%2C%20Devi%2C%20Mohammed%20and%20Khalid%20believe%20that%20something%20triggered%20a%20change%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHifz%20Ur%20Rehman%2C%20another%20local%2C%20traces%20the%20trigger%20to%20a%20video%20uploaded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EMonu%20Manesar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20anti-Muslim%20social%20me