What%20is%20a%20cloud%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20a%20window%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20up%20into%20the%20sky.%20They%20had%20no%20idea.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20education%20system%20is%20all%20about%20mugging%20things%20and%20putting%20them%20down.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179905%2Findia-new-education-preschool-primary-curriculum-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERote%20learning%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20itself%20a%20dangerous%20thing%2C%20it%20imparts%20no%20skills%20to%20students.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20rigid%20architecture%20psychologically.%20As%20a%20teacher%2C%20your%20job%20is%20to%20manage%20a%20classroom%20of%20100%20students%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20teaching%20them%2C%20just%20handling%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20classrooms%2C%20the%20person%20who%20sits%20in%20the%20back%20row%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20clown.%20Others%20do%20not%20collaborate%20with%20them.%20Whenever%20a%20backbencher%20stands%20up%2C%20everyone%20bursts%20into%20laughter%2C%20that%20student%20starts%20thinking%20they%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98joker%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20lose%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20led%20Rennis%20and%20Imma%20(whom%20he%20met%20in%20JNU)%20to%20start%20Ignis%20Careers%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20and%20his%20team%20have%20taught%20English%20language%20and%20life%20skills%20to%20over%203.5%20lakh%20students%20in%20about%201%2C000%20low-cost%20schools.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326821%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERennis%20and%20his%20team%20have%20taught%20English%20language%20and%20life%20skills%20to%20over%203.5%20lakh%20students%20in%20about%201%2C000%20low-cost%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20classrooms%20fun%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20they%20work%2C%20Rennis%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20form%20a%20small%20group%20of%20say%20five%20students.%20We%20let%20them%20sit%20in%20a%20circle%2C%20not%20rows%20so%20that%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20a%20front%20and%20a%20back-bencher.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20a%20few%20groups%20of%204-5%20students%20each.%20We%20then%20ask%20one%20group%20to%20design%20a%20smart%20village%20with%20the%20best%20sustainable%20technology%20possible%2C%20we%20ask%20another%20group%20to%20redesign%20a%20hospital.%20They%20observe%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20current%20system%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20design%20which%20they%20draw%20on%20a%20chart.%20While%20doing%20that%2C%20they%20build%20design%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20promote%20positive%20interaction%20among%20peers.%20It%20helps%20them%20to%20build%20critical%20awareness%20and%20negotiations%20among%20team%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C